179void prcsub_trayinfo_need_renewal(int force)
180{
181 if ((force != 0) || (callback_generation_status & PRSUB_CALLBACK_TRAY_INFO)) {
182 if (di_get_trayinfo(&di_tinfo) != 0) { /* ¥È¥ì¥¤¾ğÊó¼èÆÀ */
183 ASSERT(0);
184 }
185 callback_generation_status &= ~PRSUB_CALLBACK_TRAY_INFO;
186 }
187}
188void di_event_trayinfo_need_renewal(void)
189{
190
191 callback_generation_status |= PRSUB_CALLBACK_TRAY_INFO;
192#if 0
193 printf("di_event_trayinfo_need_renewal\n");
194#endif
195}

197/************************************************************************
198 * __itoa:WIN32¤ÇÄó¶¡¤µ¤ì¤ë´Ø¿ô¤Îµ¡Ç½¤ò¤Ş¤Í¤ë
199 * »ÃÄêÅª¤Ê¤â¤Î¤Ê¤Î¤Ç10 ¿Ê¿ô°Ê³°¤ÏÊİ¾Ú¤Ç¤­¤Ê¤¤
200 *
201 ************************************************************************
202 */
203
204#ifndef GPS
205#define MINUS 0x2D
206static unsigned char *__itoa(int decimal, unsigned char *buffer, int radix)
207{
208 unsigned long t_data, keta;
209 unsigned long keta_chi;
210 unsigned char out_word;
211 unsigned long i;
212
213
214 if (decimal < 0) { /* Éé¤Î¿ôÃÍ */
215 *buffer = MINUS;
216 buffer++;
217 decimal = ~decimal; /* Éä¹æÈ¿Å¾ */
218 decimal++;
219 }
220 for( t_data=decimal, keta =1 ; keta < 8; keta++){ /* check keta-suu */
221 if ((t_data /= radix) == 0){
222 break;
223 }
224 }
225 for( ; keta > 0 ; keta--){
226 for ( i=1, keta_chi = 1 ; i < keta; i++)
227 keta_chi *= radix;
228 out_word = decimal / keta_chi;
229 *buffer = 0x30 + out_word; /* À°¿ô¤òASCII¥³¡¼¥É¤ËÊÑ´¹ */
230 buffer++;
231 decimal -= (out_word * keta_chi);
232 }
233 *buffer++ = '\0';
234 return buffer;
235
236}
237#endif /* GPS */
238int prsub_replace_prpageinfo(environment_job_t *penv_job, environment_page_t *penv_page)
239{
240#ifdef GPS
241/*
242 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö¾ğÊó¤òÃÖ¤­´¹¤¨¤ë¡£
243 * GPS¼Âµ¡ÈÇ°Ê³°¤Ç¤ÏÉ¬Í×¤Ê¤¤¡£
244 */
245
246 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
247 int replace = 0;
248
249 ; /* ¥Ú¡¼¥¸Ëè¤Î´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¥¢¥¯¥»¥¹¤Ë»ÈÍÑ ¢¨¤¿¤À¤·¡¢¸½¾õ¤Ï¥¸¥ç¥Ö¤´¤È¤Ë¸ÇÄê*/
250
251#ifdef USE_USERFORM
252 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_MAIN);
253#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
254 pDest = prcall_get_dest();
255#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
256
257
258#if 0
259 /*
260 * RPCS¤È¤Ï°ã¤¤¡¢´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤Ï¥¸¥ç¥Ö¤ÎºÇ½é¤Î¤ß»ØÄê¤µ¤ì¤Æ¸å¤ÏÊÑ¹¹¤µ¤ì¤Ê¤¤
261 */
262 get_pageinfo(penv_page, 0, 0); /* ¥Ú¡¼¥¸ÍÑ´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤Î¼èÆÀ */
263
264#endif
265 /* IMAGEDRAWÆÃÍ­¤Î¥Ñ¥é¥á¡¼¥¿ÊäÀµ */
266 /* ´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤«¤é¼èÆÀ¤Ç¤­¤Ê¤¤¥Ñ¥é¥á¡¼¥¿¤ò°Ê²¼¤Ç¥»¥Ã¥È¤¹¤ë */
267
268 /* »æ¼ï */
269
270 if (diset.interp_id == DI_INTERP_BMLINKS) {
271 /*
272 * IMAGEDRAW¤Ç¤Ï»ØÄêÍÑ»æ¥µ¥¤¥º¤È¥¤¥á¡¼¥¸¥µ¥¤¥º¤¬É¬¤º¤·¤â°ìÃ×¤·¤Æ¤¤¤ë¤È¤Ï
273 * ¸Â¤é¤Ê¤¤¤¿¤á,¤³¤³¤ÇÅ¬ÀÚ¤ÊÍÑ»æ¥µ¥¤¥º¤Ë½¤Àµ¤¹¤ë¡£
274 */
275 adjust_pcode(penv_page, prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper_code);
276 }
277 /* ¶õ¤­¥µ¥¤¥ºÀßÄê ²£ */
278 penv_page->xoffset = pDest->page_info.offsetX;
279
280 /* ¶õ¤­¥µ¥¤¥ºÀßÄê ½Ä */
281 penv_page->yoffset = pDest->page_info.offsetY;
282
283 /* */
284// if (pDest->page_info.paper_count >= 1) { TIFFDPÂĞ±ş
285// 4/19 suzuki START
286#if 0
287 if ((pDest->page_info.paper_count >= 1) || ( RtiffIF.Copies >= 1 )) {
288 /*
289 * Ê£¿ôÉô¿ô»ØÄê¤¬¤¢¤ë
290 * ´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤Ï¾å½ñ¤­¤µ¤ì¤ë¡£
291 */
292// penv_page->paper_count = pDest->page_info.paper_count;
293 penv_page->paper_count = (pDest->page_info.paper_count > RtiffIF.Copies )?
294 pDest->page_info.paper_count : RtiffIF.Copies ;
295 }
296#endif
297// 4/19 suzuki END
298 /*
299 * £±¥Ú¡¼¥¸ÌÜ¤Î¥Ú¡¼¥¸¾ğÊó¤òÊİÂ¸¤·¤Æ¤ª¤­¡¢¼¡¥Ú¡¼¥¸°Ê¹ß¤Î°õºşÊı¸ş¤¬ÊÑ¹¹¤µ¤ì¤¿¾ì¹ç¤Ë
300 * °õºş¤µ¤ì¤ëÍÑ»æ¤¬Æ±¤¸¤â¤Î¤Ë¤Ê¤ë¤è¤¦¤ËÄ´À°¤¹¤ë¡£
301 */
302 if (pDest->page_info.no == 1) {
303 /*
304 * ¤³¤Î¥¸¥ç¥Ö¤ÎºÇ½é¤Î¥Ú¡¼¥¸
305 *
306 */
307 MEMCOPY(&pDest->job_paper, &pDest->page_info.paper, sizeof (imagedraw_paper_info_t));
308 replace = pDest->page_info.paper.flag;
309 }
310 else {
311 /*
312 * ¾ğÊó¤ÎÈæ³Ó¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
313 */
314 if (pDest->page_info.paper.flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_ID) {
315 unsigned char old_id;
316 unsigned char new_id;
317
318 old_id = pDest->job_paper.id;
319 new_id = pDest->page_info.paper.id;
320 if ((old_id == new_id)) {
321 DBGMSG2(("pDest->job_paper.id %d, pDest->page_info.paper.id %d\n", pDest->job_paper.id, pDest->page_info.paper.id));
322#if 0 /* */
323 pDest->page_info.paper.id = pDest->job_paper.id;
324 penv_page->paper_code = pDest->job_paper.id;
325 if (pDest->job_paper.id != pDest->page_info.paper.id) {
326 penv_page->data_is_rotated = 1;
327 }
328 else {
329 penv_page->data_is_rotated = 0;
330 }
331#endif
332 }
333 else {
334 MEMCOPY(&pDest->job_paper, &pDest->page_info.paper,
335 sizeof (imagedraw_paper_info_t));
336 replace |= IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_ID;
337 replace |= IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_SIZE;
338 }
339 }
340 }
341
342 /*
343 * ¥¢¥×¥êÁØ¤«¤é¤Î»æ¼ï»ØÄê¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
344 *
345 */
346 if (replace & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_ID) {
347 penv_page->paper_code = pDest->page_info.paper.id;
348 }
349 if (replace & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_KIND) {
350 /*
351 * »æ¼ï»ØÄê¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
352 * ´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤Ï¾å½ñ¤­¤µ¤ì¤ë¡£
353 */
354 penv_page->paper_type = pDest->page_info.paper.kind;
355 }
356 if (replace & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_SIZE) {
357 /*
358 * »æ¥µ¥¤¥º»ØÄê¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
359 * ´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤Ï¾å½ñ¤­¤µ¤ì¤ë¡£
360 */
361 if (penv_page->paper_code == DI_CODE_FREEmm) {
362 penv_page->is_custom = TRUE;
363 } else {
364 penv_page->is_custom = FALSE;
365 }
366 penv_page->paper_width = pDest->page_info.paper.width;
367 penv_page->paper_length = pDest->page_info.paper.length;
368 }
369 if (replace & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_TRAY_ID) {
370 penv_page->input_tray = pDest->page_info.paper.tray_id;
371 }
372
373#ifdef USE_IMAQ
374 /*
375 * °õºş¥â¡¼¥É»ØÄê¤¬¤¢¤ë
376 */
377 if (replace & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_PRTMODE) {
378 penv_page->prtmode = pDest->page_info.paper.prtmode;
379 }
380 else {
381 penv_page->prtmode = prcall_ext_info_ptr->prtmode;
382 }
383 /*
384 * 2005.03.02 °¤Éô
385 * »æ¼ï¥°¥ë¡¼¥×¤ÎÃÍ¤Ï¤È¤ê¤¢¤¨¤º»æ¼ï¤ò»ØÄê¤¹¤ë¤³¤È¤Ë¤Ê¤Ã¤¿¡£
386 */
387 penv_page->pkgroup = penv_page->paper_type;
388#endif /* USE_IMAQ */
389 dump_envpage( penv_page );
390#endif /* GPS */
391 return 0;
392}

394extern struct option Rtiffoptions[] ;
395#define OPTION_CHECK( _i_ ) (Rtiffoptions[ _i_ ].flag & OPT_USER)
396
397int prsub_set_prjobinfo(void)
398{
399#ifdef GPS
400/*
401 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö¾ğÊó¤òÀßÄê¤¹¤ë
402 * GPS¼Âµ¡ÈÇ°Ê³°¤Ç¤ÏÉ¬Í×¤Ê¤¤¡£
403 */
404
405 prfunc_call_t *pr_func;
406 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
407
408 pr_job_info_t prjobinfo ;
409 environment_job_t *env_job;
410
411 extern struct optionPara OptionData ; /* 2008/05/08 h.funaki */
412#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
413 int airprintflag;
414 airprintflag = checkAirPrint();
415#endif
416#ifdef DEBUG_JOBINFO
417 PRINTF("START jobinfo\n");
418#endif
419#ifdef USE_USERFORM
420 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_MAIN);
421#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
422 pDest = prcall_get_dest();
423#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
424 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
425
426
427 get_jobinfo(&pDest->env_job, FALSE);
428 get_pageinfo(&pDest->env_page, 0, 0);
429 /* ¥Õ¥é¥°¤Î¥»¥Ã¥È */
430 MEMZERO(&prjobinfo, sizeof(pr_job_info_t));
431
432 env_job = &pDest->env_job;
433
434// TIFFDPÂĞ±ş:Î¾ÌÌ°õºş
435 env_job->outmode = PR_OUT_IMGINFO ;
436 if ( RtiffIF.RtiffON ) {
437 if ( RtiffIF.Bothside ) {
438 env_job->is_duplex = 1 ;
439 env_job->flag |= PR_PARAM_BINDING ;
440 env_job->flag |= PR_PARAM_OUTMODE ;
441 }
442 else {
443 env_job->is_duplex = 0 ;
444 env_job->flag ^= PR_PARAM_BINDING ;
445 env_job->flag ^= PR_PARAM_OUTMODE ;
446
447 }
448 }
449
450 prjobinfo.flag |= PR_JOBINFO_IS_DUPLEX ;
451
452 if (env_job->is_duplex)
453 prjobinfo.flag |= PR_JOBINFO_IS_DUPLEX ;
454 else
455 prjobinfo.flag ^= PR_JOBINFO_IS_DUPLEX ;
456
457 if (env_job->do_image_skip)
458 prjobinfo.flag |= PR_JOBINFO_IS_IMAGE_SKIP ;
459 if (env_job->panelout_rotated)
460 prjobinfo.flag |= PR_JOBINFO_IS_PANELOUT_ROTATED ;
461
462 prjobinfo.job_id = aspara.job_id ;
463
464 /* gps_pageparam_t ¤Î¥á¥ó¥Ğ¤Î¥»¥Ã¥È */
465 prjobinfo.para = env_job->flag; /* Ì¾Á°ÊÑ¤ï¤Ã¤Æ¤¤¤ëÅÀ¤ËÃí°Õ */
466// prjobinfo.qty = env_job->qty;
467 /* 2008/05/08 h.funaki
468 PJL=OFF¤Î»ş¤Ï¡¢QTY¤Ë1¤òÀßÄê */
469 prjobinfo.para |= PR_PARAM_QTY ;
470#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
471 if (airprintflag) {
472 prjobinfo.qty = env_job->qty ;
473 }
474 else
475#endif /* USE_MP_TIFF */
476 {
477 /* °õºş¥ª¥×¥·¥ç¥ó¤Ê¤Î¤Çemlqty¤¬Í¥ÀèÅÙ¤¬£±ÈÖ¹â¤¤ */
478 if (OptionData.emlqty) {
479 prjobinfo.qty = env_job->qty ;
480 }
481 /* qty¤Î»ØÄê¤¬¤¢¤ê¡¢pjl=on¤¬Ìµ¤¤¾ì¹ç¤À¤±¡¢¶¯À©Åª¤Ë1¤È¤¹¤ë¡£ */
482 else if ( (OPTION_CHECK(OPT_PJL_QTY) != 0) && (OptionData.pjl == 0) ) {
483 prjobinfo.qty = 1 ;
484 }
485 else {
486 /* PJL¥³¥Ş¥ó¥É¤òÍ­¸ú¤È¤¹¤ë¤¿¤á¡¢´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤«¤éÀßÄê¤¹¤ë¡£ */
487 prjobinfo.qty = env_job->qty ;
488 }
489 }
490 prjobinfo.outmode = env_job->outmode;
491
492 /*
493 * Î¾ÌÌÄÖ¤¸Êı¸ş¤òÊÑ¹¹¤¹¤ë
494 * SHORTEDGE,LONGEDGE¤¬»ØÄê¤µ¤ì¤Æ¤¤¤ë¾ì¹ç¤ÏÊÑ´¹¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
495 */
496 if (env_job->binding == PR_BIND_BOTTOM) {
497 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper_direction != 0) {
498 /* PRINTF("LANDs\n"); */
499 env_job->binding = PR_BIND_TOP; /* ¾å¤¬Ä¹ÊÕ¤Ê¤Î¤Ç¾åÄÖ¤¸¤ËÊÑ¹¹ */
500 }
501 else {
502 /* PRINTF("PORT\n"); */
503 env_job->binding = PR_BIND_LEFT; /* º¸¤¬Ä¹ÊÕÄÖ¤¸¤Ê¤Î¤Çº¸ÄÖ¤¸¤ËÊÑ¹¹ */
504 }
505 }
506
507 if (env_job->binding == PR_BIND_LEFTRIGHT) {
508 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper_direction != 0) {
509 /* PRINTF("LANDS\n"); */
510 env_job->binding = PR_BIND_LEFT;
511 }
512 else {
513 /* PRINTF("PORT\n"); */
514 env_job->binding = PR_BIND_TOP;
515 }
516 }
517
518// TIFFDPÂĞ±ş
519 /* Î¾ÌÌ°õºş Ymargin Xmargin¤ÎÂĞ±ş 2008/05/08 h.funaki */
520 if (( RtiffIF.RtiffON ) && ( RtiffIF.Bothside )) {
521 if ( RtiffIF.Bothside == 2 ) {
522 env_job->binding = PR_BIND_TOP ; // ¾åÄÖ¤¸
523 env_job->margin1v = RtiffIF.Ymargin ;
524 env_job->margin2v = RtiffIF.Ymargin * -1;
525 env_job->margin1h = RtiffIF.Xmargin ;
526 env_job->margin2h = RtiffIF.Xmargin ;
527 }
528 else {
529// env_job->binding = PR_BIND_LEFT ; // ²£ÄÖ¤¸

1097 }
1098 else
1099#endif /* USE_MP_TIFF */

1125 notdef_flag = getUrfPHead_PrVal(URF_PAGEHEAD_STAPLE, &pr_val);
1126 if (notdef_flag && !((res == 1) && ipp_fidelity)) {
1127 pageinfo2.staple = pr_val;

1132#endif /* USE_MP_TIFF */

1177 dummy = memset(&pageinfo_shm, 0x00, sizeof(pageinfo_shm));

1183 }
1184 else {

1218 }
1219 else {

1222 }
1223 else {

1234 /* ¥×¥ê¥ó¥¿¥¹¥¿¥ó¥× */
1235 pageinfo_shm.stamp = RtiffIF.PjlPrinterStamp ;

1239#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF

1249 if (res == PR_ERROR) {
1250 return 1;
1251 }
1252 }
1253// 2006/05/26 END
1254
1255
1256 return 0;
1257}

1259unsigned char prcall_get_currenttray_paperkind(void){
1260 extern BYTE in_tray[];
1261 extern LONG CurrentTray_Logical;
1262 unsigned long p_kind;
1263 unsigned char gw_pkind;

1266 extern UBYTE get_gw_pkind(UBYTE);

1268

1270 if(p_kind == MEDIA_NONE){

1272 }

1274
1275 return gw_pkind;
1276}

1300 MEMZERO(&pDest->adv_func, sizeof (pDest->adv_func ));

1304 if (adv_fnc < LIBIMAGEDRAW_ADV_FUNC_NUM) {

1310/*
1311 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³ÈÄ¥µ¡Ç½¤ÎÈ¿±Ç

1313 * ¤Ê¤ª¡¢³ºÅöµ¡Ç½¤¬¼Âµ¡¾å¤ÇÌµ¸ú¤Ë¤Ê¤Ã¤Æ¤¤¤ë¾ì¹ç¤Ë¤Ï¡¢»ØÄê¤µ¤ì¤¿µ¡Ç½¤Ï²ò½ü¤¹¤ë¡£
1314 *
1315 */
1316
1317#define GIPA_MEMORY_SIZE (15 * 1024 * 1024)
1318void prsub_set_job_advanced_function(prif_dest_ptr pDest)
1319{
1320 prfunc_call_t *pr_func;
1321 int result;
1322
1323 DBG_MSG_PRCALL(("prcall_set_job_advanced_function\n"));
1324 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
1325
1326
1327 if (pr_func->setaccelerationmode != NULL) {
1328 /*
1329 * HW¥¢¥¯¥»¥é¥ì¡¼¥·¥ç¥ó¤ÎÀßÄê´Ø¿ôÍ­¤ê
1330 * ¥³¥ó¥È¥í¡¼¥é¤Î¹½À®¤Ë¤è¤ê¡¢µ¡Ç½¤ÎÍ­¸úÌµ¸ú¤¬¤¢¤ë¤¬
1331 * 04A-05A¤Ş¤Ç¤ÎHW¥¢¥¯¥»¥é¥ì¡¼¥·¥ç¥ó¤Ç¤¢¤ëIPA¤Ï mipsµ¡¼ï¤ÎÌ¤ÂĞ±ş¤Î¤¿¤á
1332 * ½èÍı¤¬Ìµ¸ú¤È¤Ê¤Ã¤Æ¤¤¤ë¤È´Ø¿ô¤Î¥¢¥É¥ì¥¹¤¬¥¯¥ê¥¢¤µ¤ì¤Æ¤¤¤ë¡£
1333 */
1334 unsigned long flag;
1335
1336 flag = FALSE;
1337 if (pDest->adv_func.flag & __ADVANCED_FUNC_MASK_HWA) {
1338 /*
1339 * HW¥¢¥¯¥»¥é¥ì¡¼¥¿¤Î»ÈÍÑÍ×µá¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
1340 */
1341#ifdef GPS
1342 if (check_HW_acceleration(pDest->job_info.bitSw [BIT_SW_007]) == __ADVANCED_FUNC_RESULT_ON) {
1343 flag = PR_TRUE; /* ÀßÄê¾ò·ïÍ­¸ú */
1344 }
1345#endif /* GPS */
1346 }
1347 result = pr_func->setaccelerationmode(pDest->prh, flag,
1348 GIPA_MEMORY_SIZE / 1024);
1349 if (result != PR_OK) {
1350 __ERROR("HW accelerator request");
1351#ifdef DEBUG_PRCALL_ERROR_REPORT
1352 PRINTF("setaccelerationmode error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
1353#endif
1354 }
1355 }
1356 else {
1357 /* HW¥¢¥¯¥»¥é¥ì¡¼¥·¥ç¥ó¤¬Ìµ¸ú¤Ê¤Î¤Ç¡¢»ØÄê¥Ó¥Ã¥È¤Ï¥¯¥ê¥¢¤¹¤ë¡£ */
1358 pDest->adv_func.flag &= ~__ADVANCED_FUNC_MASK_HWA;
1359 }
1360

1368/*

1374#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
1375int prcall_write_start_job(int panel_ret,
1376 int panel_status,

1383{

1394#endif /* USE_TME_STAT */

1397#else

1400 pDest->page_info.no = 0; /* ¥¸¥ç¥ÖÃæ¤Î½èÍı¥Ú¡¼¥¸¿ô½é´ü²½ */

1403 * ¥Ó¥Ã¥È¥¹¥¤¥Ã¥Á¤Î¼èÆÀ
1404 */
1405 for (i = 0; i < LIBIMAGEDRAW_BITSW_NUM; i++) {
1406 result = di_get_bitswinfo(i, &flag);
1407 if (result == 0) {
1408 pDest->job_info.bitSw [i] = (unsigned char)flag;
1409 }
1410 else {
1411 pDest->job_info.bitSw [i] = 0;
1412
1413 }
1414 }

1422 if((panel_ret == DI_PCND_SHM_OK) &&
1423 (panel_status == DI_PCND_SHM_STATUS_COND) &&
1424 ((panel_job_type == DI_PCND_MEDIAPRINTJOB) ||
1425 (panel_job_type == DI_PCND_THUMBNAILJOB )) &&

1428 case DI_PCND_DUPLEX_OFF:
1429 OptionData.bothside = SIDE_SIMPLEX;
1430 RtiffIF.Bothside = OptionData.bothside;
1431 break;
1432 case DI_PCND_DUPLEX_LEFT:
1433 OptionData.bothside = SIDE_DUPLEX;
1434 RtiffIF.Bothside = OptionData.bothside;
1435 break;
1436 case DI_PCND_DUPLEX_TOP:
1437 OptionData.bothside = SIDE_FLIP;
1438 RtiffIF.Bothside = OptionData.bothside;
1439 break;
1440 default:
1441 break;

1449 result = prsub_set_prjobinfo();
1450 if (result != 0)
1451 return result;
1452 /* ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³ÈÄ¥µ¡Ç½Í×µá */
1453 prsub_set_job_advanced_function(pDest);

1999 {

2011#endif /* USE_USERFORM */

2015}
2016#ifdef DEBUG_IMAGE_CHECK /* ÉÁ²è¥Ç¡¼¥¿ ¥Ç¥³¡¼¥É°Û¾ï¤Î¥Á¥§¥Ã¥¯ */
2017void prsub_image_check(prif_dest_ptr pDest)
2018{
2019 unsigned long i;
2020 unsigned char *buffer_ptr;
2021 unsigned char b,g,r;
2022 unsigned char sb,sg,sr;
2023
2024 b = 0; g= 0; r=0;
2025 sb = 0; sg= 0; sr=0;
2026 buffer_ptr = pDest->buffer [0];
2027 for (i = 0; i < pDest->page_info.image_width; i++) {
2028
2029 b = *buffer_ptr;
2030 buffer_ptr++;
2031 g = *buffer_ptr;
2032 buffer_ptr++;
2033 r = *buffer_ptr;
2034 buffer_ptr++;
2035 if ((sb == b) && (sr == r) && (sg == g))
2036 continue;
2037 if ((b != g) || (g != r) || (r != b)) {
2038// printf("b = %02x, g = %02x, r = %02x\n", b,g,r);
2039 sb = b;
2040 sr = r;
2041 sg = g;
2042 }
2043
2044 }
2045}
2046#endif /* DEBUG_IMAGE_CHECK */

2082// TIFFDPå¯¾å¿œ
2083// flag = PR_STRBLT_RGB;
2084 if (pDest->page_info.source_info.components == 1) {
2085 flag = PR_STRBLT_MONO;
2086 }
2087 else {
2088 flag = PR_STRBLT_RGB;
2089 }
2090
2091 }
2092
2093#ifdef DEBUG_STRETCHBLT
2094 DBG_MSG3X_PRCALL("prcall_write_band_image_draw line addr ", line_count, pDest->buffer [0]);
2095#endif
2096
2097 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
2098#if 0 /* prcall_write_start_page_image_drawã§ãƒãƒ³ãƒ‰ã‚¹ã‚¿ãƒ¼ãƒˆã™ã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ã«å¤‰æ›´ã™ã‚‹ã€‚ */
2099 /* ãƒãƒ³ãƒ‰ã‚¤ãƒ¡ãƒ¼ã‚¸ã®æç”» æœ€åˆã®ãƒãƒ³ãƒ‰ã®æ™‚ã«ã¯å€¤ã‚’ï¼ã«ã™ã‚‹ */
2100 if (pDest->band_no == -1) {
2101 pDest->band_no = 0;
2102 pr_func->bandstart(pDest->prh, pDest->band_no);
2103 }
2104#endif
2105#ifdef DEBUG_IMAGE_CHECK /* æç”»ãƒ‡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ ãƒ‡ã‚³ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ç•°å¸¸ã®ãƒã‚§ãƒƒã‚¯ */
2106 prsub_image_check(pDest);
2107#endif /* DEBUG_IMAGE_CHECK */
2108
2109#ifdef USE_CMOST
2110/*
2111 * CMOSTãŒæœ‰åŠ¹ãªå€ç‡ãŠã‚ˆã³è¡Œæ•°ã®å ´åˆã«ã¯ã€CMOST ONã§å‡¦ç†ã‚’è¡Œã†ã€‚
2112 * å°†æ¥çš„ã«ã¯ã€ç’°å¢ƒå¤‰æ•°ã§ON/OFFæŒ‡å®šãŒè¡Œãˆã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ã«å¤‰æ›´ã™ã‚‹
2113 * æ¡ä»¶ï¼š å€ç‡ ï¼•å€ä»¥ä¸Š
2114 * ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ³æ•° ï¼•ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ³ä»¥ä¸Š
2115 */
2116 if ((pDest->page_info.zoom >= 5) && (line_count > 5)) {
2117 flag |= PR_STRBLT_ZOOMCMOST;
2118 }
2119
2120#endif /* USE_CMOST */
2121
2122 /* 1ãƒã‚¤ãƒˆãƒãƒ³ãƒ€ãƒªã«è¨­å®š 2007/02/09 */
2123 /* 4ãƒã‚¤ãƒˆãƒãƒ³ãƒ€ãƒªã«è¨­å®š 2007/03/27 */
2124 flag |= PR_STRBLT_ALIGN_4BYTE ;
2125
2126 for (i = 0; i < pDest->page_info.destnation_info.copies; i++) {
2127 /* ç”»åƒé ˜åŸŸã”ã¨ã«ç¸¦æ–¹å‘ã®å¤‰å€ç‡ã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã—ã€æç”»ä½ç½®ãƒ»é«˜ã•ã‚’è¨ˆç®—ã™ã‚‹ */
2128 float henbairitu = (float)position->h/(float)pDest->page_info.source_info.length;
2129 int cur_line, prev_line, one_time_fill_line;
2130
2131 if(pDest->page_info.destnation_info.control & DESTNATION_CONTROL_MINUS){
2132 /*
2133 * StretchBltã¯å¤©åœ°é€†é †ã®ã‚¤ãƒ¡ãƒ¼ã‚¸ã¯ã§ããªã„ãŸã‚ã€å¤©åœ°é€†é †ã®è¤‡æ•°ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ³ãƒ‡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã®å ´åˆã¯ã€
2134 * ï¼‘ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ³å˜ä½ã«åˆ†è§£ã—ã¦æç”»ã™ã‚‹å¿…è¦ãŒã‚ã‚‹ãŒã€
2135 * ç¾çŠ¶å¤©åœ°é€†é †ã¯BMPã®ã¿ã§ã€å…¨ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ³ãƒ‡ã‚³ãƒ¼ãƒ‰æ™‚ã¯æ­£è¦–æ–¹å‘ã§æ ¼ç´ã—ãªãŠã—ã€
2136 * å…¨ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ³ä¸å¯ã®ã¨ãã¯ï¼‘ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ³ãƒ‡ã‚³ãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã«ã—ã¦ã„ã‚‹ã€‚
2137 * å‡¦ç†ã‚’ç°¡ä¾¿ã«ã™ã‚‹ãŸã‚ã€ã“ã“ã§ã¯å¤©åœ°é€†é †ã®æ™‚ã¯ï¼‘ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ³ã®ã¿ã«é™å®šã™ã‚‹ã€‚(æˆ¸ç”°)
2138 */
2139 ASSERT(line_count == 1);
2140 prev_line = (int)(henbairitu *
2141 (float)(pDest->page_info.source_info.length - pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no));
2142 cur_line = (int)(henbairitu *
2143 (float)(pDest->page_info.source_info.length - pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no + line_count));
2144 one_time_fill_line = cur_line - prev_line;
2145 } else {
2146 cur_line = (int)(henbairitu * pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no);
2147 if (pDest->buffer_height > 0) {
2148 prev_line = (int)(henbairitu *
2149 (pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no -
2150 pDest->buffer_height));
2151 } else {
2152 prev_line = (int)(henbairitu *
2153 (pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no -
2154 line_count));
2155 }
2156
2157 one_time_fill_line = cur_line - prev_line;
2158 }
2159 if(one_time_fill_line == 0){
2160 continue; /* DestãŒï¼‘ãƒ©ã‚¤ãƒ³ã«æº€ãŸãªã„æ™‚ã¯ã‚¹ã‚­ãƒƒãƒ— */
2161 }
2162
2163 /* Image rotatin setting. */
2164 if (!((model_distinct == MODEL_WIDE) &&
2165 (OptionData.pjl_imagedirection
2166 == DI_ENV_VAL_INT_IMAGEDIRECTION_REVERSE))) {
2167 if (( RTIFF_YOKO_KAITEN )||(RTIFF_TATE_KAITEN)) {
2168 flag |= PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_270 ;
2169 }
2170 }
2171 else {
2172 /* 180 degree image rotation by RTIFF. */
2173 if (( RTIFF_YOKO_KAITEN )||(RTIFF_TATE_KAITEN)) {
2174 flag |= PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_90;
2175 }
2176 else {
2177 flag |= PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_180;
2178 }
2179 prev_line = position->h - prev_line - one_time_fill_line;
2180 }
2181
2182 /*
2183 * ã‚¯ãƒªãƒƒãƒ—ã®æŒ‡å®š
2184 */
2185
2186 if ( ( ( clip->sx > position->x ) /* å§‹ç‚¹sx,syã®ç¯„å›²å¤–*/
2187 || (clip->sy > position->y))
2188 || ((clip->ex < (position->x + position->w)) /* çµ‚ç‚¹ex,eyã®ç¯„å›²å¤–*/
2189 || (clip->ey < (position->y + position->h)))
2190 ) {
2191 result = pr_rectangle(pDest->prh, PR_ALTCLIP, clip->sx, clip->sy, clip->ex, clip->ey);
2192 if (result != PR_OK) {
2193 PRINTF("rectangle error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
2194 }
2195 }
2196
2197// 2006/09/21 h.funaki depth=4 ã®æ™‚ã¯ã€å¤šå€¤ç”»åƒã®æç”»
2198// if (pDest->page_info.source_info.depth == 8) {
2199 if ((pDest->page_info.source_info.depth == 8) ||
2200 (pDest->page_info.source_info.depth == 4)) {
2201
2202 /* å›è»¢ã®å¯¾å¿œ position->y + prev_lineâ‡”position->x
2203 position->wâ‡”one_time_fill_line ã®å…¥ã‚Œæ›¿ãˆã‚’è¡Œã† */
2204 if ( ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_90) ||
2205 ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_270 ) ) {
2206
2207 result = pr_func->stretchblt(pDest->prh, flag,
2208 pDest->page_info.source_info.width, line_count,
2209 position->y + prev_line, position->x,
2210 one_time_fill_line, position->w,
2211 pDest->buffer[0], 0);
2212 }
2213 else {
2214 result = pr_func->stretchblt(pDest->prh, flag,
2215 pDest->page_info.source_info.width, line_count,
2216 position->x, position->y + prev_line,
2217 position->w, one_time_fill_line,
2218 pDest->buffer[0], 0);
2219 }
2220
2221 }
2222 else {
2223#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
2224 if (pDest->buffer_height > 0) {
2225 if ( ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_90) ||
2226 ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_270 ) ) {
2227 result = pr_func->stretchblt_index(pDest->prh,
2228 flag|PR_STRBLT_1BPP|PR_STRBLT_INDEX_ON,
2229 pDest->page_info.source_info.width,
2230 line_count,
2231 position->y + prev_line,
2232 position->x,
2233 line_count * 2,
2234 pDest->page_info.source_info.width * 2,
2235 pDest->buffer [0], &mono_index_tbl [0], 0);
2236 }
2237 else {
2238 result = pr_func->stretchblt_index(pDest->prh,
2239 flag|PR_STRBLT_1BPP|PR_STRBLT_INDEX_ON,
2240 pDest->page_info.source_info.width,
2241 line_count,
2242 position->x,
2243 position->y + prev_line,
2244 pDest->page_info.source_info.width * 2,
2245 line_count * 2,
2246 pDest->buffer [0], &mono_index_tbl [0], 0);
2247 }
2248 } else
2249#endif /* USE_MP_TIFF */
2250 /* å›è»¢ã®å¯¾å¿œ position->y + prev_lineâ‡”position->x
2251 position->wâ‡”one_time_fill_line ã®å…¥ã‚Œæ›¿ãˆã‚’è¡Œã† */
2252 if ( ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_90) ||
2253 ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_270 ) ) {
2254 result = pr_func->stretchblt_index(pDest->prh, flag|PR_STRBLT_1BPP|PR_STRBLT_INDEX_ON ,
2255 pDest->page_info.source_info.width, line_count,
2256 position->y + prev_line, position->x,
2257 one_time_fill_line, position->w,
2258 pDest->buffer [0], &mono_index_tbl [0], 0);
2259 }
2260 else {
2261
2262 result = pr_func->stretchblt_index(pDest->prh, flag|PR_STRBLT_1BPP|PR_STRBLT_INDEX_ON ,
2263 pDest->page_info.source_info.width, line_count,
2264 position->x, position->y + prev_line,
2265 position->w, one_time_fill_line,
2266 pDest->buffer [0], &mono_index_tbl [0], 0);
2267 }
2268 }
2269 if (result != PR_OK) {
2270 PRINTF("stretchblt error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
2271 }
2272 result = pr_resetclip(pDest->prh);
2273 if (result != PR_OK) {
2274 PRINTF("resetclip error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
2275 }
2276 position++;
2277 clip++;
2278 }
2279#ifdef DEBUG_LINE
2280 PRINTF("lineno %d->%d \n", pDest->page_info.destnation_info.offset, pDest->page_info.destnation_info.offset+line_count);
2281#endif /* DEBUG_LINE */
2282 return ;
2283}
2284
2285#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
2286void prcall_write_end_page_image_draw(prif_dest_ptr pDest)
2287#else
2288void prcall_write_end_page_image_draw(prif_dest_ptr pDest, int output_mode)
2289#endif
2290{
2291
2292 prfunc_call_t *pr_func;
2293 unsigned long status;
2294 int result;
2295 unsigned long jobreset;
2296 DBG_MSG_PRCALL("prcall_write_end_page_image_draw\n");
2297
2298 status = prcall_get_internal_status();
2299 /*
2300 * ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–é–‹å§‹ä¸­ã®ã¿å‡¦ç†ã‚’è¡Œã†ã€‚
2301 * ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–é–‹å§‹ãŒOFFã®å ´åˆã¯ã€ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–ãƒªã‚»ãƒƒãƒˆã¾ãŸã¯ã‚¨ãƒ©ãƒ¼ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–ãƒªã‚»ãƒƒãƒˆç™ºç”Ÿ
2302 */
2303
2304 if (status & PRCALL_STATUS_JOBSTART) {
2305 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
2306 result = pr_func->bandend(pDest->prh);
2307 if (result != PR_OK) {
2308 jobreset = prcall_check_job_reset();
2309 if (jobreset != 0) {
2310 __ERROR("PRCALL_STATUS_JOBRESET");
2311 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_JOBRESET);
2312 }
2313 else {
2314 __ERROR("PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_LIBRARY");
2315 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_LIBRARY);
2316 }
2317 }
2318 else {
2319#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
2320 /* FREE SIZEã®æ™‚ã¯ã€å¼·åˆ¶å°åˆ·ã‚’è¡Œã† */
2321 if( CheckFreeSize(0) || (CheckFreeSize(1)) ) {
2322 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, 4);
2323 }
2324 else {
2325 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, 0);
2326 }
2327#else
2328 if(output_mode == PRINT_OK) {
2329 long freesize_normal = CheckFreeSize(1);
2330 long freesize_bypass = CheckFreeSize(0);
2331
2332 if((freesize_normal == 1) || (freesize_bypass == 1)) {
2333 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, PR_PAPERFEED_FORCE);
2334 }
2335 else {
2336 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, PR_PAPERFEED_NORMAL);
2337 }
2338 } else {
2339 /* Ignore images need not to draw on the way of preview process. */
2340 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, PR_PAPERFEED_NOTPRINT);
2341 }
2342#endif
2343 }
2344
2345 }
2346
2347 return;
2348}
2349void prcall_write_end_job(void)
2350{
2351 prfunc_call_t *pr_func;
2352 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
2353 unsigned long status;
2354
2355#ifdef USE_USERFORM
2356 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_MAIN);
2357#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
2358 pDest = (prif_dest_ptr)(prcall_ext_info_ptr->dest);
2359#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
2360 status = prcall_get_internal_status();
2361 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
2362 /*
2363 * ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–é–‹å§‹ä¸­ã®ã¿å‡¦ç†ã‚’è¡Œã†ã€‚
2364 * ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–é–‹å§‹ãŒOFFã®å ´åˆã¯ã€ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–ãƒªã‚»ãƒƒãƒˆã¾ãŸã¯ã‚¨ãƒ©ãƒ¼ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–ãƒªã‚»ãƒƒãƒˆç™ºç”Ÿ
2365 */
2366 if (status & PRCALL_STATUS_JOBSTART) {
2367
2368 /* Set job cancel flags. */
2369 if (aspara.jobreset == TRUE) {
2370 /* Job was canceled by panel(GPS). */
2371 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = TRUE;
2372 }
2373#ifndef USE_MP_TIFF
2374 /* Error occurs when calling the "gpsPlotCancelLater"
2375 by the MediaPrintTIFF. */
2376 else {
2377 if ((RtiffIF.SummaryON == RTIFF_PRINT_ERROR) &&
2378 (prcall_ext_info.job_reseted == TRUE)) {
2379 /* If print error log after the job canceled by PDL. */
2380 aspara.jobreset = TRUE;
2381 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = FALSE;
2382 }
2383 }
2384#endif
2385
2386 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_JOBEND);
2387 pr_func->jobend(pDest->prh);
2388
2389 }
2390 else {
2391 /* Set job cancel flags. */
2392 /* NOTICE: When you pushed reset button after PDL had canceled job, */
2393 /* this process regard that job was canceled by PDL. */
2394 if (prcall_ext_info.job_reseted == TRUE) {
2395 /* Job was canceled by PDL. */
2396#ifndef USE_MP_TIFF
2397 int error_cnt;
2398
2399 /* Return value is curent error count + 1. */
2400 error_cnt = get_ep_no() - 1;
2401 if (!(RtiffIF.ErrPrint && (error_cnt > 0))) {
2402 /* If not print Error Log. */
2403 aspara.jobreset = TRUE;
2404 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = FALSE;
2405 }
2406#else
2407 aspara.jobreset = TRUE;
2408 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = TRUE;
2409#endif
2410 } else if (aspara.jobreset == TRUE) {
2411 /* Job was canceled by panel(GPS). */
2412 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = TRUE;
2413 } else {
2414 /* Inhibit QAC warning. */
2415 ;
2416 }
2417
2418 DBG_MSG_INTERNAL_STATUS("pr_func->abort");
2419 pr_func->abort(pDest->prh);
2420
2421 PRINTF("prcall_write_end_job no jobstart\n");
2422 }
2423
2424#ifdef USE_TIME_STAT
2425 {
2426 unsigned int ptime ;
2427
2428 ptime = get_jobtime();
2429
2430 /* 00'00"00 format */
2431 PRINTF("JOB: %d'%d\"%d (%d.%dPPM)\r\n",
2432 ptime / (60 * 100), ptime % (60 * 100) / 100, ptime % 100,
2433 (int)(60.0 * pDest->page_info.no * 100 / ptime),
2434 (int)(60.0 * pDest->page_info.no * 100 / ptime * 100) % 100);
2435 }
2436#endif
2437 return;
2438
2439
2440}
2441/*
2442 * ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–ã‚’çµ‚äº†é€šçŸ¥ã‚’è¡Œã†ã€‚
2443 */
2444void prcall_jobend(void)
2445{
2446
2447 DBG_MSG_PRCALL("prcall_jobend\n");
2448 di_close_host();
2449#ifdef USE_DI_V2
2450 di_close_ohost();
2451#endif
2452 di_notify_msg( DI_NOTIFYMSG_JOBEND, 0 ); /* DIã«ã€çµ‚äº†ã‚’é€šçŸ¥ã™ã‚‹ */
2453
2454}

2456static void set_prdevinfo( dev_info_t *di_info, pr_dev_info_t *pr_info )
2457{
2458 unsigned char info_bandsize_str[DI_MAX_VALUE_LEN];
2459 char appinfo_str[DI_MAX_VALUE_LEN];
2460 int ret_di_get_appinfo;
2461
2462 if( !di_info || !pr_info )
2463 return;
2464
2465 /* ï¼ã§åˆæœŸåŒ–ã—ã¦ãŠã */
2466 MEMZERO( pr_info, sizeof(pr_dev_info_t) );
2467
2468 /* ãƒ‡ã‚£ã‚¶ã‚­ãƒ£ãƒƒã‚·ãƒ¥ã¯è‡ªå‰ã®å€¤ã‚’ä½¿ç”¨ã™ã‚‹ã‚ˆã†ã«å¤‰æ›´ */
2469

2474 pr_info->gamma_info = di_info->gamma_info;
2475 pr_info->font_address = di_info->font_address;
2476 pr_info->font_size = di_info->font_size;

2479 pr_info->dither_cache = 128*1024; /* 128K */
2480 else
2481 pr_info->dither_cache = 500*1024; /* 500K */
2482#else /* Unix or Windows */
2483 pr_info->dither_cache = 300*1024; /* 300K */
2484#endif /* GPS */
2485

2499 pr_info->nplane = di_info->nplane;
2500 pr_info->bg_startp = di_info->bg_startp;
2501 pr_info->bg_slant = di_info->bg_slant;
2502 pr_info->ucr_startp = di_info->ucr_startp;
2503 pr_info->ucr_slant = di_info->ucr_slant;
2504 pr_info->soft_tsave = di_info->soft_tsave;
2505 pr_info->tsave_ratio = di_info->tsave_ratio;

2507#ifdef USE_EXTEND_TONERSAVING

2509#endif /* USE_EXTEND_TONERSAVING */
2510

2513 pr_info->sys_handle = di_info->sys_handle;
2514
2515 /* éåŒæœŸã«å¤‰åŒ–ã™ã‚‹ã‚¸ãƒ§ãƒ–ãƒªã‚»ãƒƒãƒˆæƒ…å ±ã‚’PRå´ã«é€šçŸ¥ã™ã‚‹ */
2516 pr_info->notified_job_resetted = &aspara.jobreset;
2517 pr_info->notified_forced_job_reset = &prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset;
2518
2519 /* CMMã§ä½¿ç”¨ã™ã‚‹ãƒ—ãƒ­ãƒ•ã‚¡ã‚¤ãƒ«æƒ…å ±ã‚’PRå´ã«çŸ¥ã‚‰ã›ã‚‹ */
2520 pr_info->profaddress = di_info->profaddress;
2521 pr_info->profnumber = di_info->profnumber;
2522
2523 /* WiSh-GCRå¯¾å¿œ 2007/05/17 h.funaki */
2524< #ifndef TARGET_KIBO

2526 pr_info->gcrhgr_info = (pr_gcrinfo_t *)di_info->gcrhgr_info;
2527< #endif

2530 pr_info->maxbandheight = di_info->maxbandheight ;

2532#ifdef USE_IMAQ

2534 pr_info->mode_num = di_info->resonum;
2535 pr_info->bgucr_info = (pr_bgucrinfo_t **)(di_info->bgucr_info);

2539 pr_info->pqtc = di_info->support_drop;
2540#ifdef DEBUG_PR_SETDEVINFO
2541 PRINTF("pr_info->dither_cache %08xh\n", pr_info->dither_cache);
2542 PRINTF("pr_info->dither_info %08xh\n", pr_info->dither_info);
2543#ifdef DEBUG_GAMMA_INFO

2555 PRINTF("pr_info->ucr_startp %08xh\n", pr_info->ucr_startp);

2560 {
2561 int i;
2562 pr_tlimit_info_t *pr_tlimit;
2563
2564 if (pr_info->tlimit_val != 0) {

2566 for (i = 0; i < pr_info->tlimit_num; i++, pr_tlimit++) {
2567 PRINTF("TLIMIT %d #############################################\n", i+1);

2578 PRINTF(" phot %08d\n", pr_tlimit->phot);
2579 PRINTF(" fill %08d\n", pr_tlimit->fill);
2580 }
2581 }
2582 }
2583#ifdef DEBUG_RESO
2584 {
2585 resolution_info_t *reso_ptr;
2586 int i;
2587
2588 reso_ptr = devinfo.reso_set;
2589 for (i = devinfo.resonum; i > 0; i--, reso_ptr++) {
2590 PRINTF("RESOLUTION%d #############################################\n", i);
2591 PRINTF("reso_ptr->x %d\n", reso_ptr->x);
2592 PRINTF("reso_ptr->y %d\n", reso_ptr->y);
2593 PRINTF("reso_ptr->bit %d\n", reso_ptr->bit);
2594#ifdef USE_IMAQ

2596 PRINTF("reso_ptr->dit_mode %08d\n", reso_ptr->dit_mode);
2597 PRINTF("reso_ptr->prt_mode %08d\n", reso_ptr->prt_mode);
2598#endif
2599
2600
2601 }
2602 }
2603#endif
2604 PRINTF("pr_info->sys_handle %xh\n", pr_info->sys_handle);
2605 PRINTF("pr_info->notified_job_resetted %xh\n", pr_info->notified_job_resetted);
2606 PRINTF("pr_info->notified_forced_job_reset %xh\n", pr_info->notified_forced_job_reset);
2607 PRINTF("pr_info->profaddress %xh\n", pr_info->profaddress);
2608 PRINTF("pr_info->profnumber %0h\n", pr_info->profnumber);
2609
2610#ifdef USE_IMAQ

2612 if (pr_info->flag & DI_SUPPORT_EXT_DEVINFO_PARAM) {

2618 PRINTF("pr_info->pqtc %dh\n", pr_info->pqtc);

2621

2624/*
2625 * æ©Ÿèƒ½ï¼šå°åˆ·ãƒ‘ãƒ©ãƒ¡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã®åˆæœŸåŒ–
2626 * å†…éƒ¨è¨­å®šã•ã‚Œã¦ã„ã‚‹åˆæœŸåŒ–ãƒ‘ãƒ©ãƒ¡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã‚’å°åˆ·æ™‚ãƒ‘ãƒ©ãƒ¡ãƒ¼ã‚¿ã«åæ˜ ã•ã›ã‚‹ã€‚
2627 */
2628prif_dest_ptr prcall_write_init_prif(void)
2629{
2630
2631 int pos_type;
2632 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
2633 int scaling_factor;
2634 double d_scaling_factor;
2635
2636 /* Create module interface object, fill in method pointers */
2637#ifdef USE_USERFORM
2638 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_MAIN);
2639#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
2640 pDest = (prif_dest_ptr)(prcall_ext_info_ptr->dest);
2641#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
2642
2643 /*
2644 * å°åˆ·é–¢é€£æƒ…å ±è¨­å®š ï¼ˆæ‹¡å¤§ã€å›è»¢ã€è§£åƒåº¦ï¼‰
2645 */
2646
2647 if ((prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_zoom > MODE_ZOOM_MAX)
2648 || (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_zoom == 0))
2649 pDest->page_info.zoom = 1;
2650 else
2651 pDest->page_info.zoom = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_zoom;
2652 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_rotate > MODE_ROTATE_MAX)
2653 pDest->page_info.rotate = 0;
2654 else
2655 pDest->page_info.rotate = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_rotate;
2656
2657 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_dpix != 0)
2658 pDest->page_info.dpix = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_dpix;
2659 else
2660 pDest->page_info.dpix = 600;
2661
2662 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_dpiy != 0)
2663 pDest->page_info.dpiy = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_dpiy;
2664 else
2665 pDest->page_info.dpiy = 600;
2666
2667 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_depth != 0)
2668 pDest->page_info.depth = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_depth;
2669 else
2670 pDest->page_info.depth = 1; /* USE 1bit depth */
2671
2672 ASSERT(prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_plane != 0);
2673 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_plane != 0)
2674 pDest->page_info.plane = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_plane;
2675
2676 /*
2677 * åˆæœŸçŠ¶æ…‹ã®ãƒšãƒ¼ã‚¸æƒ…å ±ã¯ãƒšãƒ¼ã‚¸ã®ã‚µã‚¤ã‚ºã€ãƒ‡ã‚¹ãƒˆãƒãƒ¼ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ³ã®ã‚µã‚¤ã‚ºã‚’è¨­å®š
2678 * ãƒ‡ã‚¹ãƒˆãƒãƒ¼ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ³ã®ã‚µã‚¤ã‚ºã¯ã€åˆæœŸå€¤ã¯ç”¨ç´™ã®ã‚µã‚¤ã‚ºã¨åŒã˜ã«ã™ã‚‹ã€‚
2679 * ã‚½ãƒ¼ã‚¹ã®ã‚µã‚¤ã‚ºã«ã¤ã„ã¦ã¯ã€ãƒ‡ã‚³ãƒ¼ãƒ‰å´ã§ã‚½ãƒ¼ã‚¹ã®ã‚µã‚¤ã‚ºã‚’è¨­å®šã™ã‚‹ã€‚
2680 */
2681 d_scaling_factor = (double)pDest->page_info.dpiy / 600.0 ;
2682
2683 /* Page size and page margin setting */
2684 if ( RtiffIF.RtiffON ) {
2685 unsigned long paper_w, paper_h;
2686 unsigned long paper_marginx, paper_marginy;
2687 long page_w, page_h;
2688 long page_offx, page_offy;
2689 int free_marginx, free_marginy;
2690 int leftsp, rightsp, uppsp, lowsp;
2691 int fRot180;
2692 int fBackSide;
2693 extern struct optionPara OptionData;
2694
2695 paper_w = prcall_ext_info_ptr->width * d_scaling_factor;
2696 paper_h = prcall_ext_info_ptr->length * d_scaling_factor;
2697 paper_marginx = prcall_ext_info_ptr->marginX * d_scaling_factor;
2698 paper_marginy = prcall_ext_info_ptr->marginY * d_scaling_factor;
2699
2700 leftsp = OptionData.leftspace;
2701 rightsp = OptionData.rightspace;
2702 uppsp = OptionData.upperspace;
2703 lowsp = OptionData.lowerspace;
2704
2705 free_marginx = 0;
2706 free_marginy = 0;
2707
2708 fRot180 = (model_distinct == MODEL_WIDE) &&
2709 (OptionData.pjl_imagedirection
2710 == DI_ENV_VAL_INT_IMAGEDIRECTION_REVERSE);
2711
2712 fBackSide = (RtiffIF.Ctr_bothside == PR_FACE_DPX1ST) &&
2713 (pDest->env_job.paper_code == pDest->env_page.paper_code) &&
2714 (pDest->env_job.paper_type == pDest->env_page.paper_type);
2715
2716 if ( !RtiffIF.MaxArea ) {
2717 if (leftsp < 0) {
2718 leftsp = 0;
2719 }
2720 if (rightsp < 0) {
2721 rightsp = 0;
2722 }
2723 if (uppsp < 0) {
2724 uppsp = 0;
2725 }
2726 if (lowsp < 0) {
2727 lowsp = 0;
2728 }
2729
2730 /* Delete margin from printing area when paper size is free. */
2731 if (IS_PAPER_FREE(RtiffIF.Ptype) ||
2732 IS_PAPER_FREE_TESASI(RtiffIF.Ptype) ||
2733 ((RtiffIF.Ptype >= PAPER_S1) && (RtiffIF.Ptype <= PAPER_S9))) {
2734 free_marginx = ROLL_FREE_MARGINX * d_scaling_factor;
2735 free_marginy = ROLL_FREE_MARGINY * d_scaling_factor;
2736 }
2737 }
2738 if ( ( RTIFF_YOKO_KAITEN ) || ( RTIFF_TATE_KAITEN ) ) {
2739 page_w = paper_w - (lowsp + uppsp + free_marginy);
2740 page_h = paper_h - (rightsp + leftsp + free_marginx);
2741
2742 if (!fRot180) {
2743 /* 270 degree image rotation */
2744 if (!fBackSide) {
2745 page_offx = paper_marginx + uppsp;
2746 page_offy = paper_marginy + rightsp;
2747 }
2748 else {
2749 if (RtiffIF.Bothside == SIDE_DUPLEX) {
2750 page_offx = paper_marginx + uppsp;
2751 page_offy = paper_marginy + leftsp;
2752 }
2753 else {
2754 page_offx = paper_marginx + lowsp;
2755 page_offy = paper_marginy + rightsp;
2756 }
2757 }
2758 }
2759 else {
2760 /* 90 degree image rotation */
2761 page_offx = paper_marginx + lowsp;
2762 page_offy = paper_marginy + leftsp;
2763 }
2764 }
2765 else {
2766 page_w = paper_w - (rightsp + leftsp + free_marginx);
2767 page_h = paper_h - (lowsp + uppsp + free_marginy);
2768
2769 if (!fRot180) {
2770 /* Image no rotation */
2771 if (!fBackSide) {
2772 page_offx = paper_marginx + leftsp;
2773 page_offy = paper_marginy + uppsp;
2774 }
2775 else {
2776 if (RtiffIF.Bothside == SIDE_DUPLEX) {
2777 page_offx = paper_marginx + rightsp;
2778 page_offy = paper_marginy + uppsp;
2779 }
2780 else {
2781 page_offx = paper_marginx + leftsp;
2782 page_offy = paper_marginy + lowsp;
2783 }
2784 }
2785 }
2786 else {
2787 /* 180 degree image rotation */
2788 page_offx = paper_marginx + rightsp;
2789 page_offy = paper_marginy + lowsp;
2790 }
2791 }
2792 if (page_w < 0) {
2793 pDest->page_info.width = 0;
2794 }
2795 else {
2796 pDest->page_info.width = page_w;
2797 }
2798 if (page_h < 0) {
2799 pDest->page_info.height = 0;
2800 }
2801 else {
2802 pDest->page_info.height = page_h;
2803 }
2804 pDest->page_info.offsetX = page_offx;
2805 pDest->page_info.offsetY = page_offy;
2806
2807 if (!RtiffIF.MaxArea) {
2808 if (!fBackSide) {
2809 if (OptionData.leftspace < 0) {
2810 RtiffIF.OffsetX += OptionData.leftspace ;
2811 }
2812 if (OptionData.upperspace < 0) {
2813 RtiffIF.OffsetY += OptionData.upperspace ;
2814 }
2815 }
2816 else {
2817 if (RtiffIF.Bothside == SIDE_DUPLEX) {
2818 if (OptionData.rightspace < 0) {
2819 RtiffIF.OffsetX += OptionData.rightspace ;
2820 }
2821 if (OptionData.upperspace < 0) {
2822 RtiffIF.OffsetY += OptionData.upperspace ;
2823 }
2824 }
2825 else {
2826 if (OptionData.leftspace < 0) {
2827 RtiffIF.OffsetX += OptionData.leftspace ;
2828 }
2829 if (OptionData.lowerspace < 0) {
2830 RtiffIF.OffsetY += OptionData.lowerspace ;
2831 }
2832 }
2833 }
2834 }
2835
2836 }
2837 else {
2838 pDest->page_info.width = (double)prcall_ext_info_ptr->width * d_scaling_factor;
2839 pDest->page_info.height = (double)prcall_ext_info_ptr->length * d_scaling_factor;
2840 pDest->page_info.offsetX = (double)prcall_ext_info_ptr->marginX * d_scaling_factor;
2841 pDest->page_info.offsetY = (double)prcall_ext_info_ptr->marginY * d_scaling_factor;
2842 }
2843
2844#if 0
2845printf( "---------------------------------------\n" ) ;
2846printf( " pDest->page_info.width:%d\n", pDest->page_info.width ) ;
2847printf( " pDest->page_info.height:%d\n", pDest->page_info.height ) ;
2848printf( " pDest->page_info.offsetX:%d\n", pDest->page_info.offsetX ) ;
2849printf( " pDest->page_info.offsetY:%d\n", pDest->page_info.offsetY ) ;
2850printf( "---------------------------------------\n" ) ;
2851#endif
2852
2853 if (di_get_trayinfo(&di_tinfo) != 0) { /* ãƒˆãƒ¬ã‚¤æƒ…å ±å–å¾— */
2854 ASSERT(0);
2855 }
2856#ifdef USE_STAPLE_POS_LOCATION
2857 /*
2858 * ãƒšãƒ¼ã‚¸ã”ã¨ã®ç”¨ç´™ã‚µã‚¤ã‚ºæƒ…å ±ã«ã‚ˆã‚Šã€ã‚¹ãƒ†ãƒ¼ãƒ—ãƒ«æ™‚ã®å›è»¢åˆ¶å¾¡ã‚’è¡Œã†æƒ…å ±ã‚’è¨­å®šã™ã‚‹ã€‚
2859 * ç¾çŠ¶ã§ã¯ã€ãƒãƒ¼ãƒ‰ã§90åº¦ã€270åº¦å›è»¢å¯èƒ½ãªæ©Ÿç¨®ã§ã¯ã€ã“ã®æƒ…å ±ã¯ä½¿ç”¨ã—ãªã„
2860 */
2861 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->staple_pos_location != 0)
2862 pDest->page_info.staple_rotate_info = prcall_ext_info_ptr->staple_pos_rotate_container + prcall_ext_info_ptr->staple_pos_location;
2863 else
2864 pDest->page_info.staple_rotate_info = NULL;
2865#ifdef DEBUG_STAPLE_POS_LOCATION
2866 {
2867 const rotate_info_t *rotate_pos;
2868
2869 rotate_pos = pDest->page_info.staple_rotate_info;
2870 if (rotate_pos != NULL) {
2871 PRINTF("staple pos1 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[0]);
2872 PRINTF("staple pos2 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[1]);
2873 PRINTF("staple pos3 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[2]);
2874 PRINTF("staple pos4 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[3]);
2875 PRINTF("staple pos5 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[4]);
2876 PRINTF("staple pos6 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[5]);
2877 PRINTF("staple pos7 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[6]);
2878 PRINTF("staple pos8 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[7]);
2879 }
2880 }
2881#endif /* DEBUG_STAPLE_POS_LOCATION */
2882
2883#endif
2884
2885 /*
2886 * ç”¨ç´™æƒ…å ±ã®è¨­å®šã‚’è¡Œã†ã€‚
2887 */
2888 pDest->page_info.paper.flag = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.flag;
2889 pDest->page_info.paper.tray_id = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.tray_id;
2890 pDest->page_info.paper.id = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.id;
2891 pDest->page_info.paper.kind = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.kind;
2892 pDest->page_info.paper.length = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.length;
2893 pDest->page_info.paper.width = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.width;
2894 pDest->page_info.paper.direction = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.direction;
2895#ifdef DEBUG_PAPER_DETAIL_INFORMATION
2896 PRINTF("paper.flag 0x%04xd\n", pDest->page_info.paper.flag);
2897 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_TRAY_ID) {
2898 PRINTF("tray_id %02d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.tray_id);
2899 }
2900 PRINTF("id %02d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.id);
2901 PRINTF("kind 0x%02x\n", pDest->page_info.paper.kind);
2902 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_SIZE) {
2903 PRINTF("length %d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.length);
2904 PRINTF("width %d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.width);
2905 }
2906 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_DIRECTION) {
2907 PRINTF("direction %d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.direction);
2908 }
2909#endif /* DEBUG_STAPLE_POS_LOCATION */
2910
2911 pDest->page_info.image_profile = prcall_ext_info_ptr->image_profile;
2912 pDest->page_info.graphics_profile = prcall_ext_info_ptr->graphics_profile;
2913 pDest->page_info.text_profile = prcall_ext_info_ptr->text_profile;
2914 pDest->page_info.line_profile = prcall_ext_info_ptr->line_profile;
2915
2916 return pDest; /* åˆæœŸåŒ–æˆåŠŸ */
2917
2918}
2919/*
2920 * ãƒšãƒ¼ã‚¸æ¯ã«ã‹ã‚ã‚‹æƒ…å ±ã‚’è¨­å®šã™ã‚‹
2921 */
2922
2923/*
2924 * æŒ‡å®šã—ãŸè§£åƒåº¦ã®æƒ…å ±ã‚’å–å¾—ã™ã‚‹
2925 * å…¥åŠ› : è§£åƒåº¦ãƒ“ãƒƒãƒˆæ·±ã•ã®ãƒ†ãƒ¼ãƒ–ãƒ«
2926 * ãƒ†ãƒ¼ãƒ–ãƒ«ã®å€‹æ•°
2927 * å‡ºåŠ› å°åˆ·å“è³ªã«å¯¾ã™ã‚‹è§£åƒåº¦ãƒ†ãƒ¼ãƒ–ãƒ«ã¸ã®ãƒã‚¤ãƒ³ã‚¿
2928 * å¾©å¸°æƒ…å ± 0:æ­£å¸¸ -1:è©²å½“ã™ã‚‹æƒ…å ±ãŒç„¡ã„
2929 */
2930int prsub_get_reso_set(
2931 resolution_info_t *reso_set,
2932 int reso_num,
2933 int mode,
2934 resolution_info_t **reso_ptr)
2935{
2936#ifdef USE_IMAQ
2937 int i;
2938 int max = 0;
2939 int reso_bit;
2940 int found = 0;
2941
2942 unsigned char kind;
2943 resolution_info_t *tmp_reso_set;
2944
2945 if (!reso_set || !reso_ptr || !reso_num){
2946 return -1;
2947 }
2948 tmp_reso_set = reso_set;
2949 kind = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.kind;
2950#ifdef DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY
2951 PRINTF(" prsub_get_reso_set param\n");
2952 PRINTF(" kind %d,reso_num %d, mode %d\n", kind, reso_num, mode);
2953
2954#endif /* DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY */
2955 if (kind == 0xff) {
2956 /*
2957 * ä¸‡ãŒä¸€ã“ã“ã¾ã§ã®é–“ã«ç´™ç¨®ãŒæ±ºå®šã—ã¦ã„ãªã‹ã£ãŸã‚‰
2958 * æ™®é€šç´™ï¼å†ç”Ÿç´™ã‚’è¨­å®šã™ã‚‹ã€‚
2959 */
2960 __ERROR("prsub_get_reso_set NO PAPER SELECT\n");
2961 kind = DI_PAPER_AUTO;
2962 }
2963 for (i = 0; i < reso_num; i++, tmp_reso_set++) {
2964#ifdef DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY
2965 PRINTF("SEARCH PRINT QUALITY %d\n", i + 1);
2966 PRINTF(" ->x %d\n", tmp_reso_set->x);
2967 PRINTF(" ->y %d\n", tmp_reso_set->y);
2968 PRINTF(" ->bit %d\n", tmp_reso_set->bit);
2969 PRINTF(" ->prt_mode %d\n", tmp_reso_set->prt_mode);
2970 PRINTF(" ->paper %d\n", tmp_reso_set->paper);
2971#endif /* DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY */
2972 if (tmp_reso_set->paper == kind) {
2973 /*
2974 * ç´™ç¨®ãŒåŒã˜ã‚‚ã®ãŒã‚ã£ãŸ
2975 */
2976#ifdef DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY
2977 PRINTF("PAPER TYPE FOUND %d,kind %d\n", i+1, kind);
2978#endif /* DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY */

2990 found = 1;
2991 break;

2997 max = reso_bit;
2998 found = 1;
2999 }
3000 }

3002

3006 * è©²å½“ã™ã‚‹ã‚‚ã®ãŒè¦‹ã¤ã‹ã‚‰ãªã‹ã£ãŸã€‚

3090
3091void prsub_get_colorprofile(unsigned char kind, unsigned long *vividness,
3092 unsigned long *gradation, unsigned long *text)
3093{
3094 int i, j, k;
3095 int di_result = DI_PINI_ERROR;
3096 char pini_key[16];
3097 char pini_parameter[32];
3098 char workarea[16];
3099 long pini_kind;
3100
3101 if((vividness == NULL) || (gradation == NULL) || (text ==NULL)){
3102 return;
3103 }
3104
3105 for(i = 1; ; i++){
3106
3107 sprintf(pini_key, "colorprofile%d", i);
3108 di_result = di_get_appinfo(pini_key,"IDP",&pini_parameter[0]);
3109
3110 if(di_result != DI_PINI_OK){
3111 break;
3112 }
3113
3114 /* Pick paper kind. */
3115 for(j = 0, k = 0; pini_parameter[k] != ',' ; j++, k++){
3116 workarea[j] = pini_parameter[k];
3117 }
3118 workarea[j] = '\0';
3119 pini_kind = strtol(workarea, NULL, 16);
3120 k++;
3121
3122 if((pini_kind == kind) || (i == 1)){
3123 /* Pick vividness. */
3124 for(j = 0; pini_parameter[k] != ',' ; j++, k++){
3125 workarea[j] = pini_parameter[k];
3126 }
3127 workarea[j] = '\0';
3128 *vividness = strtol(workarea, NULL, 16);
3129 k++;
3130
3131 /* Pick gradation. */
3132 for(j = 0; pini_parameter[k] != ',' ; j++, k++){
3133 workarea[j] = pini_parameter[k];
3134 }
3135 workarea[j] = '\0';
3136 *gradation = strtol(workarea, NULL, 16);
3137 k++;
3138
3139 /* Pick text. */
3140 for(j = 0; pini_parameter[k] != '\0' ; j++, k++){
3141 workarea[j] = pini_parameter[k];
3142 }
3143 workarea[j] = '\0';
3144 *text = strtol(workarea, NULL, 16);
3145
3146 if(pini_kind == kind){
3147 break;
3148 }
3149 }
3150 }
3151}

3427static int prsub_init(void)
3428{

4603{

4605 if( size == 0 ) {
4606 prcall_free(data_ptr);
4607 return NULL;
4608 }

4615 ((prif_dest_ptr)(prcall_ext_info_ptr->dest))->prh,
4616 (unsigned char*)data_ptr,

4620#endif /* DEBUG_MEMORY */

4912 * 92:¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥È¤·¤Ş¤·¤¿
4913 * P5:¼õ¿®Ãæ»ß
4914 * ¤Î½çÈÖ¤Ç¥í¥°¤¬»Ä¤Ã¤Æ¤¤¤ë¡£
4915 * ¤³¤ì¤ÏÀè¤Ë¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥È¤Ã¤¬È¯À¸¤·¤Æ¤¤¤ë¤¬¡¢PDL¤¬¸¡ÃÏ¤·¤Ê¤¤¤¦¤Á¤Ë
4916 * ¥Ç¡¼¥¿¤¬ÅÓÀÚ¤ì¤¿¤³¤È¤ò¼¨¤·¤Æ¤¤¤ë¡£
4917 * ¥ì¥¢¥±¡¼¥¹¤Ç¤¢¤ë¤¬¡¢Àµ¾ï¤ËÆ°ºî¤¹¤ë¤è¤¦¤Ë½¤Àµ¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
4918 * ½èÍıÅª¤Ë¤Ï¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥È¤¬¸«¤Ä¤«¤Ã¤¿¤é¥¹¥Æ¡¼¥¿¥¹¤Î¾å½ñ¤­¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
4919 */
4920 if (prcall_check_job_reset() != 0) {
4921 DBG_MSG_JOBRESET("status replace PRCALL_STATUS_ABORT-->PRCALL_STATUS_JOBRESET");
4922 status = PRCALL_STATUS_JOBRESET;
4923 }
4924 }
4925 switch (status) {
4926 case PRCALL_STATUS_ABORT:
4927 di_notify_msg(DI_NOTIFYMSG_ERRFORCE, IMAGEDRAW_ERROR_ABBORT);
4928 data_reset = 0;
4929 break;
4930 case PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_DATA:
4931 case PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_IO:
4932 case PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_LIBRARY:
4933 case PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_DECODE:
4934 /*
4935 * 2004.11.04. °¤Éô
4936 * ¡ÖÍÑ»æ¥µ¥¤¥º¥¨¥é¡¼¡×
4937 * ¡ÖÉÁ²èÎÎ°è¤ÎÏÀÍıÌ·½â¡×

4939 * ¥¨¥é¡¼¥¹¥Æ¡¼¥¿¥¹¤È¤·¤ÆÄÉ²Ã¤¹¤ë
4940 */

4945 break;
4946 case PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_MEMORY:
4947 di_notify_msg(DI_NOTIFYMSG_ERRFORCE, IMAGEDRAW_ERROR_MEMORYERROR);
4948 break;

4950 /*
4951 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥È¤Ï´û¤ËÉ½¼¨¤µ¤ì¤Æ¤¤¤ë¤Î¤Ç¥¨¥é¡¼É½¼¨¤Ï¤·¤Ê¤¤
4952 */
4953 break;
4954 case PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_REQUEST:
4955 /*
4956 * ²¿¤é¤«¤Î¥¨¥é¡¼È¯À¸
4957 * ¥¨¥é¡¼É½¼¨¤·¤Ê¤¤¤¬¡¢¥Ç¡¼¥¿¥­¥ã¥ó¥»¥ëÃæ¤ÎÉ½¼¨¤Î¤ßGPS¤Ë¼Â¹Ô¤µ¤»¤ë¡£

4959 * GJµ¡¼ï¤Ç¤ÎOHP¥â¥Î¥¯¥í°õºş°õºşÉÔ²Ä»ş¤Î¥ê¥»¥Ã¥È½èÍı

4961 break;

4973// break;

4976 break;
4977 }
4978 /*
4979 * 2003/03/28 °¤Éô
4980 * ¥ª¡¼¥È¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥È¤Î»ş¤Ë¤Ï¡¢GPSÂ¦¤Ë¥Ç¡¼¥¿¤òÇÑ´ş¤·¤¿»İ¤òÅÁ¤¨¤ëÉ¬Í×¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
4981 * GPS¤Ç¤ÏÌµ¤¯¤Æ¤â¥¨¥é¡¼ÍúÎò¤¬¹Ô¤ï¤ì¤ë¤¬¡¢nGPS¤Ç¤Ï»ÅÍÍ¤¬ÊÑ¹¹¤µ¤ì¤¿¡£
4982 * EOFÄÌÃÎ¤Ë¤è¤ë¥ª¡¼¥È¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥È¤Ç¤âÇÑ´ş¤·¤¿»İ¤òÅÁ¤¨¤ë¡£

4985 */
4986 if (status != PRCALL_STATUS_JOBRESET) {
4987 di_notify_msg(DI_NOTIFYMSG_STATE, DI_INTERP_STATE_FLUSHING);
4988 }
4989 }
4990 else {
4991 /*
4992 * ´û¤Ë¥¨¥é¡¼¤¬È¯À¸¤·¤Æ¤¤¤ë¾ì¹ç¤Ë¤Ï¡¢¥Ç¡¼¥¿¤ÏÆÉ¤ß¼Î¤Æ¤ëÉ¬Í×¤¬Ìµ¤¤
4993 */
4994 data_reset = 0;
4995 }
4996 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->status & PRCALL_STATUS_JOBSTART) {
4997 if ((status & PRCALL_STATUS_JOBRESET) == 0) {
4998 prcall_ext_info.job_reseted = TRUE;
4999 }
5000 }
5001 /*
5002 * Àè¤Ë¥¨¥é¡¼¥¹¥Æ¡¼¥¿¥¹¤òÀßÄê¤·¤Æ¤ª¤¯
5003 */
5004 prcall_ext_info_ptr->status = status;
5005 if (data_reset == 1) {
5006 /*
5007 * EOF¤Ş¤¿¤Ï¥¿¥¤¥à¥¢¥¦¥È¤Ş¤ÇÆÉ¤ß¼Î¤Æ¤ë
5008 */
5009 DBG_MSG_JOBRESET("data discard start");
5010 reset_job();
5011 DBG_MSG_JOBRESET("data discard end\n");
5012 }
5013 }
5014 else {
5015 /*
5016 * Àµ¾ï°õºş»ş¤Î¥¹¥Æ¡¼¥¿¥¹¤òÈ¿±Ç¤¹¤ë
5017 */
5018
5019 /* ¥ï¡¼¥Ë¥ó¥°¤ÎÂĞ±ş 2006/07/05 h.funaki */
5020 if ( status == PRCALL_STATUS_WARNING ) {
5021#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
5022 if (notify_warning_message) {
5023 di_notify_msg(DI_NOTIFYMSG_ERRFORCE, DI_ST_99_WARNING);
5024 }
5025#else
5026 di_notify_msg(DI_NOTIFYMSG_ERRFORCE, DI_ST_99_WARNING);
5027#endif
5028 }
5029 else {
5030 if (status == PRCALL_STATUS_DATA_WAIT) {
5031 prcall_ext_info.job_reseted = FALSE;
5032 }
5033 prcall_ext_info_ptr->status = status;
5034 if (status == PRCALL_STATUS_SEARCH_PJL) {
5035 reset_job();
5036 }
5037 }
5038 }
5039 return;
5040}

5059int prcall_check_paper_direction(imagedraw_paper_info_t *paper_request, int mode)
5060{
5061 unsigned long flag;
5062 unsigned char paper_id;
5063 unsigned char kind;
5064 environment_page_t penv_page;
5065 int stat; /* Éüµ¢¾ğÊó */
5066 int result;
5067
5068 DBG_MSG_PRCALL("prcall_check_paper_direction ");
5069
5070#ifdef GPS
5071 get_pageinfo(&penv_page, 0, 0); /* ¥Ú¡¼¥¸ÍÑ´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤Î¼èÆÀ */
5072
5073 flag = paper_request->flag; /* Í­¸ú¤Ê¾ğÊó¤ÎÀßÄê */
5074 if (flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_ID) {
5075 /*
5076 * ¥Ú¡¼¥Ñ¡¼ID»ØÄê¤¬É¬¤ºÉ¬Í×
5077 */
5078 penv_page.paper_code = paper_request->id;
5079 }else {
5080 /*
5081 * ¥Ú¡¼¥Ñ¡¼ID¤¬Ìµ¤¤¤Î¤Ï¤¢¤ê¤¨¤Ê¤¤¡£
5082 */
5083 __ERROR("prcall_check_paper_direction NO PAPER ID");
5084 return result;
5085 }
5086 if (flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_KIND) {
5087 penv_page.paper_type = paper_request->kind;
5088 kind = paper_request->kind;
5089 }
5090 else {
5091 penv_page.paper_type = DI_PAPER_AUTO;
5092 kind = PRCALL_PAPER_TYPE_ALLRANGE_SELECT; /* »æ¼ï¤Ë¤è¤é¤º¸¡º÷¤¹¤ë */
5093 }
5094 if (flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_SIZE) {
5095 /*
5096 * »æ¥µ¥¤¥º»ØÄê¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
5097 * ´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤Ï¾å½ñ¤­¤µ¤ì¤ë¡£
5098 */
5099 penv_page.paper_width = paper_request->width;
5100 penv_page.paper_length = paper_request->length;
5101 }
5102 if (flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_TRAY_ID) {
5103 penv_page.input_tray = paper_request->tray_id;
5104 }
5105#ifdef DEBUG_PENV
5106 PRINTF("*********************************************************\n");
5107 dump_envpage(&penv_page);
5108 PRINTF("*********************************************************\n");
5109#endif
5110 prcsub_trayinfo_need_renewal(1);
5111 stat = check_paper_direction(&penv_page, &di_tinfo, kind, mode);
5112 if ((mode != 0) && (stat != PRCALL_PAPER_DIRECTION_NOTFOUND)) {
5113 /*
5114 * ¾ğÊó¤Î¾å½ñ¤­»ØÄê¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
5115 */
5116 paper_request->kind = penv_page.paper_type;
5117
5118 if ((flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_ID) == 0) {
5119 if (penv_page.input_tray != DI_TRAY_AUTO) {
5120 /*
5121 *
5122 */
5123 paper_request->tray_id = penv_page.input_tray;
5124 }
5125 }
5126 }
5127#else
5128 /*
5129 * ¼Âµ¡°Ê³°¤Ç¤Ï¡¢¾ï¤Ë»ØÄêÊı¸ş¤ÎÍÑ»æ¤¬¤¢¤ë¤³¤È¤òÄÌÃÎ¤¹¤ë¡£
5130 */
5131 stat = PRCALL_PAPER_DIRECTION_EXACT;
5132#endif
5133 return stat;
5134}
5135/*
5136 * ÂçÊ¸»ú->¾®Ê¸»úÊÑ´¹
5137 *} Éüµ¢¾ğÊó¡¡:'\0'¤ò´Ş¤àÊ¸»úÎó¤ÎÄ¹¤µ
5138 */
5139int prsub_convert_strings(unsigned char *dest, const unsigned char *src)
5140{
5141 int i;
5142 for (i = 0; i < 512; i++) {
5143 if ('A' <= *src && *src <= 'Z')
5144 *dest = *src + 'a' - 'A';
5145 else {
5146 *dest = *src;
5147 }
5148 if (*src == '\0')
5149 break;
5150 dest++;
5151 src++;
5152 }
5153
5154 return i;
5155
5156}
5157
5158char * prsub_strstr (const char * str1, const char * str2)
5159{
5160 char *cp = (char *) str1;
5161 char *s1, *s2;
5162
5163 if ( !*str2 )
5164 return((char *)str1);
5165
5166 while (*cp)
5167 {
5168 s1 = cp;
5169 s2 = (char *) str2;
5170
5171 while ( *s1 && *s2 && !(*s1-*s2) )
5172 s1++, s2++;
5173
5174 if (!*s2)
5175 return(cp);
5176
5177 cp++;
5178 }
5179
5180 return(NULL);
5181
5182}

5297int prcall_set_extend_data(unsigned short type, void *data)
5298{
5299 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
5300 int i;
5301 unsigned long mask;
5302 unsigned long flag;
5303 int result;
5304 /*
5305 * ¥«¥á¥é¥á¥â¤ÎÆâÍÆ¤Ï¡¢pDest¤Î³ÈÄ¥¾ğÊóÎÎ°è¤Ë³ÊÇ¼¤¹¤ë¡£
5306 */
5307#ifdef USE_USERFORM
5308 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_CURRENT); /* ¸½ºß¥«¥ì¥ó¥È¤ÎpDest¤ò¼èÆÀ¤¹¤ë¡£ */
5309#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
5310 pDest = prcall_get_dest();
5311#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
5312 mask = 0x00000ff;
5313 flag = pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_flag;
5314 result = -1;
5315 for (i = 0; i < EXTEND_DATA_SET_Area_MAX; i++) {
5316 if ((flag & mask) == 0) {
5317 pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_data [i] = (unsigned char *)data;
5318 pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_flag |= EXTEND_DATA_SET_Area(type, i);
5319 result = 0;
5320 break;
5321 }
5322 mask <<= 8;
5323 }
5324 return result;
5325}
5326void *prcall_get_extend_data(unsigned short type)
5327{
5328 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
5329 int i;
5330 unsigned long mask;
5331 unsigned char *data;
5332 unsigned short data_type;
5333 unsigned long flag;
5334
5335#ifdef USE_USERFORM
5336 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_CURRENT); /* ¸½ºß¥«¥ì¥ó¥È¤ÎpDest¤ò¼èÆÀ¤¹¤ë¡£ */
5337#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
5338 pDest = prcall_get_dest();
5339#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
5340 mask = 0x00000ff;
5341 data = NULL;
5342 flag = pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_flag;
5343 for (i = 0; i < EXTEND_DATA_SET_Area_MAX; i++) {
5344 if ((flag & mask) != 0) {
5345 data_type = EXTEND_DATA_GET_Area(flag, i);
5346 if (data_type == type) {
5347 /*
5348 * ¸½¾õIDP¤Ç¤Ï¥Ç¡¼¥¿¼ïÊÌ1¤ò¥«¥á¥é¥á¥â¾ğÊó¤È¤·¤Æ»ÈÍÑ¤¹¤ë¡£
5349 * ¥«¥á¥é¥á¥â¤Ï»ÈÍÑ¤·¤¿¤é²òÊü¤¹¤ëÉ¬Í×¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
5350 */
5351 data = pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_data [i];
5352 pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_data [i] = NULL;
5353 EXTEND_DATA_CLEAR_Area(flag, i);
5354 break;
5355 }
5356 }
5357 mask <<= 8;
5358 }
5359 if (data != NULL) {
5360 pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_flag = flag;
5361 }
5362 return data;
5363}

5414 GJµ¡¤È¤¹¤ë(°õºşÉÊ¼Á¤¢¤ê)

5435LONG CheckPrintMode( LONG dpi, LONG p_kind, LONG Quality )
5436{
5437
5438 int i;
5439 resolution_info_t *reso_ptr;
5440
5441 reso_ptr = devinfo.reso_set;
5442 /* ²òÁüÅÙ¥Æ¡¼¥Ö¥ë¤Ë»ØÄê¤µ¤ì¤¿¥Ñ¥é¥á¡¼¥¿¤ÎÁÈ¤ß¹ç¤ï¤»¤¢¤ë¤«¥Á¥§¥Ã¥¯¤¹¤ë¡£ */

5562static int _URF2PR(urf_pr table[], unsigned char urf_val, int *pr_val)
5563{
5564 int i;
5565 for(i = 0; table[i].urf != -1; i++){
5566 if(table[i].urf == urf_val){
5567 *pr_val = table[i].pr;
5568 break;
5569 }
5570 }
5571 if (table[i].urf == -1) {
5572 return 0;
5573 }
5574 else {
5575 return 1;
5576 }
5577}
5578
5579int getUrfPHead_PrVal(int urf_phead_id, int *pr_val)
5580{
5581 urfPageHead *urfPHead;
5582 extern urfPageHead *getUrfPageHeader(void);
5583 int def_flag = 0;
5584 int result;
5585 int i;
5586
5587 urfPHead = getUrfPageHeader();
5588 if ((urfPHead == NULL) || (pr_val == NULL)) {
5589 return 0;
5590 }
5591
5592 switch (urf_phead_id) {
5593 case URF_PAGEHEAD_DUPLEX:
5594 if (urfPHead->duplex == 0) {
5595 def_flag = 1;
5596 }
5597 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_duplex, urfPHead->duplex, pr_val);
5598 break;
5599 case URF_PAGEHEAD_MEDIA:
5600 if (urfPHead->media == 0) {
5601 def_flag = 1;
5602 }
5603 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_paper_type, urfPHead->media, pr_val);
5604 break;
5605 case URF_PAGEHEAD_INTRAY:
5606 if (urfPHead->intray == 0) {
5607 def_flag = 1;
5608 }
5609 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_input_tray, urfPHead->intray, pr_val);
5610 break;
5611 case URF_PAGEHEAD_OUTBIN:
5612 if (urfPHead->outbin == 0) {
5613 def_flag = 1;
5614 }
5615 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_output_tray, urfPHead->outbin, pr_val);
5616 break;
5617 case URF_PAGEHEAD_COPIES:
5618 if (urfPHead->copies == 0) {
5619 def_flag = 1;
5620 }
5621 *pr_val = urfPHead->copies;
5622 break;
5623 case URF_PAGEHEAD_STAPLE:
5624 for (i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
5625 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_staple, urfPHead->finishngs[i], pr_val);
5626 if (result) {
5627 break;
5628 }
5629 }
5630 break;
5631 case URF_PAGEHEAD_PUNCH:
5632 for (i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
5633 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_punch, urfPHead->finishngs[i], pr_val);
5634 if (result) {
5635 break;
5636 }
5637 }
5638 break;
5639 default:
5640 result = 0;
5641 break;
5642 }
5643
5644 return (result && !def_flag);
5645}

5654< for(i = 0;i

5656< (reso_set->y == reso_ptr->y) &&
5657< (reso_set->bit == reso_ptr->bit) &&

5667<
5668< static void parse_specific_reso(
5669< unsigned char *get_str_buf, resolution_info_t *reso_ptr)
5670< {
5671< unsigned char parse_str_buf[DI_MAX_VALUE_LEN];
5672< int i,j,count = 0;
5673< unsigned int reso_info[RESO_TABLE_MEM_COUNT];
5674< void *dummy;
5675<
5676< if ((get_str_buf == NULL) || (reso_ptr == NULL)) {
5677< return;
5678< }
5679<
5680< dummy = memset(reso_info,0xff,sizeof(reso_info));
5681< dummy = memset(parse_str_buf,0,sizeof(parse_str_buf));
5682<
5683< for(j=i=0 ;count
5684< if((get_str_buf[i] == ',')||(!get_str_buf[i] )){
5685< reso_info[count++] = atoi(parse_str_buf);
5686< dummy = memset(parse_str_buf,0,sizeof(parse_str_buf));
5687< j=0;
5688<
5689< if(!get_str_buf[i]){
5690< break;
5691< }
5692< }
5693< else{
5694< parse_str_buf[j++] = get_str_buf[i];
5695< }
5696< }
5697< reso_ptr->x = reso_info[0];
5698< reso_ptr->y = reso_info[1];
5699< reso_ptr->bit = (unsigned char)reso_info[2];
5700< reso_ptr->paper = (unsigned char)reso_info[3];
5701< reso_ptr->prt_mode = (unsigned char)reso_info[4];
5702< reso_ptr->dit_mode = (unsigned char)reso_info[5];
5703<
5704< return;
5705< }
5706<
5707< int get_specific_reso(int mode, resolution_info_t *reso_ptr, unsigned char kind)
5708< {
5709< unsigned char get_str_buf[DI_MAX_VALUE_LEN];
5710< unsigned char *printquality_str;
5711< unsigned char search_str_buf[DI_MAX_VALUE_LEN];
5712< int is_pini_reso;
5713< int rc;
5714< unsigned int i;
5715< int str_ret;
5716< int reso_num = devinfo.resonum;
5717< resolution_info_t *reso_set = devinfo.reso_set;
5718<
5719< switch(mode){
5720< case DI_PCND_MEDIA_PRTQUAL_NORMAL:
5721< printquality_str = "normal_reso";
5722< break;
5723<
5724< case DI_PCND_MEDIA_PRTQUAL_DRAFT:
5725< printquality_str = "draft_reso";
5726< break;
5727<
5728< case DI_PCND_MEDIA_PRTQUAL_FINE:
5729< printquality_str = "fine_reso";
5730< break;
5731<
5732< default:
5733< return LIBIMAGDRAW_RESULT_NG;
5734< }
5735<
5736< /* Search paper kind from pini. */
5737< /* Hit legacy description. */
5738< rc = di_get_appinfo(printquality_str, "IDP", &get_str_buf[0]);
5739< if((rc == DI_PINI_OK) && (reso_ptr != NULL)){ /* Inhibit Klocwork warning. */
5740< parse_specific_reso(&get_str_buf[0],reso_ptr);
5741< is_pini_reso = check_reso_set_pini(reso_num, reso_set, reso_ptr);
5742< if(is_pini_reso == LIBIMAGDRAW_RESULT_OK){
5743< return LIBIMAGDRAW_RESULT_OK;
5744< }
5745< }
5746< /* Hit new description. */
5747< rc = DI_PINI_OK;
5748< for(i = 1; rc == DI_PINI_OK; i++){
5749< str_ret = sprintf(search_str_buf, "%s%d", printquality_str, i);
5750< if(str_ret == EOF){
5751< break;
5752< }
5753< rc = di_get_appinfo(search_str_buf, "IDP", &get_str_buf[0]);
5754< if((rc == DI_PINI_OK) && (reso_ptr != NULL)){ /* Inhibit Klocwork warning. */
5755< parse_specific_reso(&get_str_buf[0],reso_ptr);
5756< is_pini_reso = check_reso_set_pini(reso_num, reso_set, reso_ptr);
5757< if((reso_ptr->paper == kind) &&
5758< (is_pini_reso == LIBIMAGDRAW_RESULT_OK)){
5759< return LIBIMAGDRAW_RESULT_OK;
5760< }
5761< }
5762< }
5763< return LIBIMAGDRAW_RESULT_NG;
5764< }

174{

177 ASSERT(0);
178 }
179 callback_generation_status &= ~PRSUB_CALLBACK_TRAY_INFO;
180 }

191/************************************************************************
192 * __itoa:WIN32¤ÇÄó¶¡¤µ¤ì¤ë´Ø¿ô¤Îµ¡Ç½¤ò¤Ş¤Í¤ë
193 * »ÃÄêÅª¤Ê¤â¤Î¤Ê¤Î¤Ç10 ¿Ê¿ô°Ê³°¤ÏÊİ¾Ú¤Ç¤­¤Ê¤¤
194 *
195 ************************************************************************
196 */
197
198#ifndef GPS
199#define MINUS 0x2D
200static unsigned char *__itoa(int decimal, unsigned char *buffer, int radix)
201{
202 unsigned long t_data, keta;
203 unsigned long keta_chi;
204 unsigned char out_word;
205 unsigned long i;
206
207
208 if (decimal < 0) { /* Éé¤Î¿ôÃÍ */
209 *buffer = MINUS;
210 buffer++;
211 decimal = ~decimal; /* Éä¹æÈ¿Å¾ */
212 decimal++;
213 }
214 for( t_data=decimal, keta =1 ; keta < 8; keta++){ /* check keta-suu */
215 if ((t_data /= radix) == 0){
216 break;
217 }
218 }
219 for( ; keta > 0 ; keta--){
220 for ( i=1, keta_chi = 1 ; i < keta; i++)
221 keta_chi *= radix;
222 out_word = decimal / keta_chi;
223 *buffer = 0x30 + out_word; /* À°¿ô¤òASCII¥³¡¼¥É¤ËÊÑ´¹ */
224 buffer++;
225 decimal -= (out_word * keta_chi);
226 }
227 *buffer++ = '\0';
228 return buffer;
229
230}
231#endif /* GPS */
232int prsub_replace_prpageinfo(environment_job_t *penv_job, environment_page_t *penv_page)
233{

243 ; /* ¥Ú¡¼¥¸Ëè¤Î´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¥¢¥¯¥»¥¹¤Ë»ÈÍÑ ¢¨¤¿¤À¤·¡¢¸½¾õ¤Ï¥¸¥ç¥Ö¤´¤È¤Ë¸ÇÄê*/

258#endif

261
262 /* »æ¼ï */
263
264 if (diset.interp_id == DI_INTERP_BMLINKS) {
265 /*

277 /* */

291// 4/19 suzuki END
292 /*
293 * £±¥Ú¡¼¥¸ÌÜ¤Î¥Ú¡¼¥¸¾ğÊó¤òÊİÂ¸¤·¤Æ¤ª¤­¡¢¼¡¥Ú¡¼¥¸°Ê¹ß¤Î°õºşÊı¸ş¤¬ÊÑ¹¹¤µ¤ì¤¿¾ì¹ç¤Ë
294 * °õºş¤µ¤ì¤ëÍÑ»æ¤¬Æ±¤¸¤â¤Î¤Ë¤Ê¤ë¤è¤¦¤ËÄ´À°¤¹¤ë¡£

296 if (pDest->page_info.no == 1) {
297 /*
298 * ¤³¤Î¥¸¥ç¥Ö¤ÎºÇ½é¤Î¥Ú¡¼¥¸
299 *
300 */
301 MEMCOPY(&pDest->job_paper, &pDest->page_info.paper, sizeof (imagedraw_paper_info_t));
302 replace = pDest->page_info.paper.flag;
303 }
304 else {
305 /*
306 * ¾ğÊó¤ÎÈæ³Ó¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
307 */
308 if (pDest->page_info.paper.flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_ID) {
309 unsigned char old_id;
310 unsigned char new_id;
311
312 old_id = pDest->job_paper.id;
313 new_id = pDest->page_info.paper.id;
314 if ((old_id == new_id)) {
315 DBGMSG2(("pDest->job_paper.id %d, pDest->page_info.paper.id %d\n", pDest->job_paper.id, pDest->page_info.paper.id));
316#if 0 /* */

338 *

356 penv_page->is_custom = TRUE;
357 } else {
358 penv_page->is_custom = FALSE;
359 }
360 penv_page->paper_width = pDest->page_info.paper.width;
361 penv_page->paper_length = pDest->page_info.paper.length;
362 }
363 if (replace & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_TRAY_ID) {
364 penv_page->input_tray = pDest->page_info.paper.tray_id;

366
367#ifdef USE_IMAQ

370 */

380 */
381 penv_page->pkgroup = penv_page->paper_type;
382#endif /* USE_IMAQ */
383 dump_envpage( penv_page );
384#endif /* GPS */

400 prif_dest_ptr pDest;

409#endif

412#endif

434 env_job->flag |= PR_PARAM_OUTMODE ;

439 env_job->flag ^= PR_PARAM_OUTMODE ;

488 * SHORTEDGE,LONGEDGE¤¬»ØÄê¤µ¤ì¤Æ¤¤¤ë¾ì¹ç¤ÏÊÑ´¹¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£

501 if (env_job->binding == PR_BIND_LEFTRIGHT) {
502 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper_direction != 0) {

522 else {
523// env_job->binding = PR_BIND_LEFT ; // ²£ÄÖ¤¸
524 env_job->binding = PR_BIND_LEFTRIGHT ; // ½Ä²£ÄÖ¤¸ 2008/01/07

537 }

539 env_job->force_tray_select = 0;
540 }
541 dump_envjob( env_job );

565 prjobinfo.margin1h = env_job->margin1h;
566 prjobinfo.margin2v = env_job->margin2v;

575printf( " prjobinfo.margin2v :%d \n", prjobinfo.margin2v ) ;
576printf( " prjobinfo.margin1h :%d \n", prjobinfo.margin1h ) ;
577printf( " prjobinfo.margin2h :%d \n", prjobinfo.margin2h ) ;
578#endif

580 /* PR¤Ë¥Ñ¥é¥á¡¼¥¿¥»¥Ã¥È */
581 DBGMSG_PRCALL(("setjobinfo start %d\n", aspara.njob_id));
582 if (pr_func->setjobinfo(pDest->prh, &prjobinfo) == PR_ERROR) {
583 PRINTF("setjobinfo error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
584 return -1;
585 }
586 DBGMSG_PRCALL(("setjobinfo end %d\n", aspara.njob_id));
587
588 /** 2007/12/20 EMLUSERCODE¤ÎÀßÄê **/
589 if ( strlen(RtiffIF.usercode) ) {
590
591 di_ujob_info_t ujobinfo ;
592

595 memcpy( ujobinfo.up.usercode, RtiffIF.usercode, DI_MAX_UPARAM_USERCODE_LEN ) ;
596
597 if ( di_set_ujobinfo( prjobinfo.job_id, &ujobinfo ) ) {
598 PRINTF("set usercode error \n");
599 return -1;
600 }
601 }
602
603
604#endif /* GPS */
605
606 return 0;
607}

1304/*
1305 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³ÈÄ¥µ¡Ç½¤ÎÈ¿±Ç
1306 * LIBIMAGEDRAW¤¬ÂĞ±ş¤¹¤ë³ÈÄ¥µ¡Ç½¤ÎÀßÄê¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
1307 * ¤Ê¤ª¡¢³ºÅöµ¡Ç½¤¬¼Âµ¡¾å¤ÇÌµ¸ú¤Ë¤Ê¤Ã¤Æ¤¤¤ë¾ì¹ç¤Ë¤Ï¡¢»ØÄê¤µ¤ì¤¿µ¡Ç½¤Ï²ò½ü¤¹¤ë¡£
1308 *
1309 */
1310
1311#define GIPA_MEMORY_SIZE (15 * 1024 * 1024)
1312void prsub_set_job_advanced_function(prif_dest_ptr pDest)
1313{
1314 prfunc_call_t *pr_func;
1315 int result;
1316
1317 DBG_MSG_PRCALL(("prcall_set_job_advanced_function\n"));
1318 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
1319
1320
1321 if (pr_func->setaccelerationmode != NULL) {
1322 /*
1323 * HW¥¢¥¯¥»¥é¥ì¡¼¥·¥ç¥ó¤ÎÀßÄê´Ø¿ôÍ­¤ê
1324 * ¥³¥ó¥È¥í¡¼¥é¤Î¹½À®¤Ë¤è¤ê¡¢µ¡Ç½¤ÎÍ­¸úÌµ¸ú¤¬¤¢¤ë¤¬
1325 * 04A-05A¤Ş¤Ç¤ÎHW¥¢¥¯¥»¥é¥ì¡¼¥·¥ç¥ó¤Ç¤¢¤ëIPA¤Ï mipsµ¡¼ï¤ÎÌ¤ÂĞ±ş¤Î¤¿¤á
1326 * ½èÍı¤¬Ìµ¸ú¤È¤Ê¤Ã¤Æ¤¤¤ë¤È´Ø¿ô¤Î¥¢¥É¥ì¥¹¤¬¥¯¥ê¥¢¤µ¤ì¤Æ¤¤¤ë¡£
1327 */
1328 unsigned long flag;
1329
1330 flag = FALSE;
1331 if (pDest->adv_func.flag & __ADVANCED_FUNC_MASK_HWA) {
1332 /*
1333 * HW¥¢¥¯¥»¥é¥ì¡¼¥¿¤Î»ÈÍÑÍ×µá¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
1334 */
1335#ifdef GPS
1336 if (check_HW_acceleration(pDest->job_info.bitSw [BIT_SW_007]) == __ADVANCED_FUNC_RESULT_ON) {
1337 flag = PR_TRUE; /* ÀßÄê¾ò·ïÍ­¸ú */
1338 }
1339#endif /* GPS */
1340 }
1341 result = pr_func->setaccelerationmode(pDest->prh, flag,
1342 GIPA_MEMORY_SIZE / 1024);
1343 if (result != PR_OK) {
1344 __ERROR("HW accelerator request");
1345#ifdef DEBUG_PRCALL_ERROR_REPORT
1346 PRINTF("setaccelerationmode error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
1347#endif
1348 }
1349 }
1350 else {
1351 /* HW¥¢¥¯¥»¥é¥ì¡¼¥·¥ç¥ó¤¬Ìµ¸ú¤Ê¤Î¤Ç¡¢»ØÄê¥Ó¥Ã¥È¤Ï¥¯¥ê¥¢¤¹¤ë¡£ */
1352 pDest->adv_func.flag &= ~__ADVANCED_FUNC_MASK_HWA;
1353 }
1354

1362/*
1363 * °õºş¤Î³«»Ï½èÍı
1364 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö¤Î³«»Ï
1365 * Éüµ¢¾ğÊó Àµ¾ï½ªÎ» :0
1366 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³«»Ï¼ºÇÔ:-1

1368#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
1369int prcall_write_start_job(int panel_ret,
1370 int panel_status,
1371 unsigned int panel_job_type,
1372 unsigned long panel_change,
1373 unsigned long panel_duplex)
1374#else
1375int prcall_write_start_job(void)
1376#endif
1377{
1378 int result;
1379 prfunc_call_t *pr_func;
1380 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
1381 int i;
1382 int flag;
1383#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
1384 extern struct optionPara OptionData;
1385#endif
1386#ifdef USE_TIME_STAT
1387 set_jobstart_time();
1388#endif /* USE_TME_STAT */
1389#ifdef USE_USERFORM
1390 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_MAIN); /* ¥¸¥ç¥Ö¤Ê¤É¤Ï¥á¥¤¥ó¤ÎpDest¤Ç½èÍı¤¹¤ë¡£ */
1391#else
1392 pDest = prcall_get_dest();
1393#endif
1394 pDest->page_info.no = 0; /* ¥¸¥ç¥ÖÃæ¤Î½èÍı¥Ú¡¼¥¸¿ô½é´ü²½ */
1395
1396 /*
1397 * ¥Ó¥Ã¥È¥¹¥¤¥Ã¥Á¤Î¼èÆÀ
1398 */
1399 for (i = 0; i < LIBIMAGEDRAW_BITSW_NUM; i++) {
1400 result = di_get_bitswinfo(i, &flag);
1401 if (result == 0) {
1402 pDest->job_info.bitSw [i] = (unsigned char)flag;
1403 }
1404 else {
1405 pDest->job_info.bitSw [i] = 0;
1406
1407 }
1408 }
1409 /* ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³«»Ï¤Î¥¹¥Æ¡¼¥¿¥¹ÀßÄê */
1410 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_JOBSTART|PRCALL_STATUS_DECODE);
1411
1412 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
1413
1414#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
1415 /* Write panel settings over print options. */
1416 if((panel_ret == DI_PCND_SHM_OK) &&
1417 (panel_status == DI_PCND_SHM_STATUS_COND) &&
1418 ((panel_job_type == DI_PCND_MEDIAPRINTJOB) ||
1419 (panel_job_type == DI_PCND_THUMBNAILJOB )) &&
1420 ((panel_change & DI_PCND_CHG_PDL) != 0)) {
1421 switch(panel_duplex) {
1422 case DI_PCND_DUPLEX_OFF:
1423 OptionData.bothside = SIDE_SIMPLEX;
1424 RtiffIF.Bothside = OptionData.bothside;
1425 break;
1426 case DI_PCND_DUPLEX_LEFT:
1427 OptionData.bothside = SIDE_DUPLEX;
1428 RtiffIF.Bothside = OptionData.bothside;
1429 break;
1430 case DI_PCND_DUPLEX_TOP:
1431 OptionData.bothside = SIDE_FLIP;
1432 RtiffIF.Bothside = OptionData.bothside;
1433 break;
1434 default:
1435 break;
1436 }
1437 }
1438#endif
1439
1440 /* ¥¸¥ç¥Ö¾ğÊó¤ÏGPS¼Âµ¡¤Î¤ßÍ­¸ú
1441 * 2005.01.13 ÄÉµ­
1442 * ´Ø¿ôÆâ¤Ç¼Âµ¡ÈÇ¤È¼Âµ¡¥ì¥¹ÈÇ¤Î½èÍı¤òÊÌ¤±¤¿¤Î¤Ç¸Æ¤Ó½Ğ¤¹ÍÍ¤ËÊÑ¹¹ */
1443 result = prsub_set_prjobinfo();
1444 if (result != 0)
1445 return result;
1446 /* ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³ÈÄ¥µ¡Ç½Í×µá */
1447 prsub_set_job_advanced_function(pDest);
1448 result = pr_func->jobstart(pDest->prh);
1449 if (result != PR_OK) {
1450#ifdef DEBUG_PRCALL_ERROR_REPORT
1451 PRINTF("job start error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
1452
1453#endif
1454 result = -1;
1455 }
1456 return result;
1457}

1464#define DRVOUT_RAS 2 /* ÄÌ¾ïRASTER */
1465#define DRVOUT_RAS_SEP 3 /* Ê¬³äRASTER */

1468int prcall_write_start_page_image_draw(prif_dest_ptr pDest)
1469{

1497 }

1500#ifndef GPS

2000 MEMZERO(&pDest_sub->page_info.source_info, sizeof (struct source_info_str));
2001 MEMZERO(&pDest_sub->page_info.destnation_info, sizeof (struct destnation_info_str));
2002 pDest_sub->buffer [0] = pDest_sub->buffer [1] = NULL;
2003 }
2004 }
2005#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
2006 }
2007
2008 return result;
2009}
2010#ifdef DEBUG_IMAGE_CHECK /* ÉÁ²è¥Ç¡¼¥¿ ¥Ç¥³¡¼¥É°Û¾ï¤Î¥Á¥§¥Ã¥¯ */
2011void prsub_image_check(prif_dest_ptr pDest)
2012{
2013 unsigned long i;
2014 unsigned char *buffer_ptr;
2015 unsigned char b,g,r;
2016 unsigned char sb,sg,sr;
2017
2018 b = 0; g= 0; r=0;
2019 sb = 0; sg= 0; sr=0;
2020 buffer_ptr = pDest->buffer [0];
2021 for (i = 0; i < pDest->page_info.image_width; i++) {
2022
2023 b = *buffer_ptr;
2024 buffer_ptr++;
2025 g = *buffer_ptr;
2026 buffer_ptr++;
2027 r = *buffer_ptr;
2028 buffer_ptr++;
2029 if ((sb == b) && (sr == r) && (sg == g))
2030 continue;
2031 if ((b != g) || (g != r) || (r != b)) {
2032// printf("b = %02x, g = %02x, r = %02x\n", b,g,r);
2033 sb = b;
2034 sr = r;
2035 sg = g;
2036 }
2037
2038 }
2039}
2040#endif /* DEBUG_IMAGE_CHECK */
2041void prcall_write_band_image_draw(prif_dest_ptr pDest, int line_count)
2042{
2043 unsigned long result;
2044 unsigned long flag;
2045 prfunc_call_t *pr_func;
2046 imagedraw_pos_t *position; /* ÉÁ²è³«»ÏºÂÉ¸ */
2047 imagedraw_clip_pos_t *clip; /* ¥¯¥ê¥Ã¥×ºÂÉ¸ */
2048 int i, genten_y;
2049 struct destnation_info_str *destinfo;
2050 extern struct optionPara OptionData;
2051
2052 destinfo = &pDest->page_info.destnation_info;
2053
2054 position = destinfo->position;
2055 clip = destinfo->clip_position;
2056
2057 /*
2058 * ¸µ²èÁü¤Î·Á¼°¤ò»ØÄê¤¹¤ë¡£MH,MMR¤Ê¤É¤Î¥â¥Î¥¯¥í²èÁü¤Ç¤Ï PR_STRBLT_MONO
2059 * ¤½¤ì°Ê³°¤Ç¤Ï¡¢ PR_STRBLT_RGB
2060 * ¥Ú¡¼¥¸¤Î·Á¼°¤Ï´Ø·¸¤Ê¤¯½èÍı¤ò¥¤¥á¡¼¥¸¤Î·Á¼°¤Ë¤Î¤ßº¸±¦¤µ¤ì¤ë¡£
2061 */
2062 if (pDest->page_info.source_info.depth == 1) {
2063 flag = PR_STRBLT_MONO;
2064#ifdef USE_IMAQ
2065 /*
2066 * GJ¥¨¥ó¥¸¥óµ¡¼ï¤Ç¤Ï
2067 */
2068 if ((devinfo.support_drop != 0) && (pDest->env_page.paper_type == DI_PAPER_OHP)) {
2069 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_REQUEST);
2070 __ERROR("PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_REQUEST");
2071 }
2072#endif
2073 }
2074 else {
2075
2076// TIFFDPÂĞ±ş
2077// flag = PR_STRBLT_RGB;
2078 if (pDest->page_info.source_info.components == 1) {
2079 flag = PR_STRBLT_MONO;
2080 }
2081 else {
2082 flag = PR_STRBLT_RGB;
2083 }
2084
2085 }
2086
2087#ifdef DEBUG_STRETCHBLT
2088 DBG_MSG3X_PRCALL("prcall_write_band_image_draw line addr ", line_count, pDest->buffer [0]);
2089#endif
2090
2091 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
2092#if 0 /* prcall_write_start_page_image_draw¤Ç¥Ğ¥ó¥É¥¹¥¿¡¼¥È¤¹¤ë¤è¤¦¤ËÊÑ¹¹¤¹¤ë¡£ */
2093 /* ¥Ğ¥ó¥É¥¤¥á¡¼¥¸¤ÎÉÁ²è ºÇ½é¤Î¥Ğ¥ó¥É¤Î»ş¤Ë¤ÏÃÍ¤ò£°¤Ë¤¹¤ë */
2094 if (pDest->band_no == -1) {
2095 pDest->band_no = 0;
2096 pr_func->bandstart(pDest->prh, pDest->band_no);
2097 }
2098#endif
2099#ifdef DEBUG_IMAGE_CHECK /* ÉÁ²è¥Ç¡¼¥¿ ¥Ç¥³¡¼¥É°Û¾ï¤Î¥Á¥§¥Ã¥¯ */
2100 prsub_image_check(pDest);
2101#endif /* DEBUG_IMAGE_CHECK */
2102
2103#ifdef USE_CMOST
2104/*
2105 * CMOST¤¬Í­¸ú¤ÊÇÜÎ¨¤ª¤è¤Ó¹Ô¿ô¤Î¾ì¹ç¤Ë¤Ï¡¢CMOST ON¤Ç½èÍı¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
2106 * ¾­ÍèÅª¤Ë¤Ï¡¢´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤ÇON/OFF»ØÄê¤¬¹Ô¤¨¤ë¤è¤¦¤ËÊÑ¹¹¤¹¤ë
2107 * ¾ò·ï¡§ ÇÜÎ¨ £µÇÜ°Ê¾å
2108 * ¥é¥¤¥ó¿ô £µ¥é¥¤¥ó°Ê¾å
2109 */
2110 if ((pDest->page_info.zoom >= 5) && (line_count > 5)) {
2111 flag |= PR_STRBLT_ZOOMCMOST;
2112 }
2113
2114#endif /* USE_CMOST */
2115
2116 /* 1¥Ğ¥¤¥È¥Ğ¥ó¥À¥ê¤ËÀßÄê 2007/02/09 */
2117 /* 4¥Ğ¥¤¥È¥Ğ¥ó¥À¥ê¤ËÀßÄê 2007/03/27 */
2118 flag |= PR_STRBLT_ALIGN_4BYTE ;
2119
2120 for (i = 0; i < pDest->page_info.destnation_info.copies; i++) {
2121 /* ²èÁüÎÎ°è¤´¤È¤Ë½ÄÊı¸ş¤ÎÊÑÇÜÎ¨¤ò·×»»¤·¡¢ÉÁ²è°ÌÃÖ¡¦¹â¤µ¤ò·×»»¤¹¤ë */
2122 float henbairitu = (float)position->h/(float)pDest->page_info.source_info.length;
2123 int cur_line, prev_line, one_time_fill_line;
2124
2125 if(pDest->page_info.destnation_info.control & DESTNATION_CONTROL_MINUS){
2126 /*
2127 * StretchBlt¤ÏÅ·ÃÏµÕ½ç¤Î¥¤¥á¡¼¥¸¤Ï¤Ç¤­¤Ê¤¤¤¿¤á¡¢Å·ÃÏµÕ½ç¤ÎÊ£¿ô¥é¥¤¥ó¥Ç¡¼¥¿¤Î¾ì¹ç¤Ï¡¢
2128 * £±¥é¥¤¥óÃ±°Ì¤ËÊ¬²ò¤·¤ÆÉÁ²è¤¹¤ëÉ¬Í×¤¬¤¢¤ë¤¬¡¢
2129 * ¸½¾õÅ·ÃÏµÕ½ç¤ÏBMP¤Î¤ß¤Ç¡¢Á´¥é¥¤¥ó¥Ç¥³¡¼¥É»ş¤ÏÀµ»ëÊı¸ş¤Ç³ÊÇ¼¤·¤Ê¤ª¤·¡¢
2130 * Á´¥é¥¤¥óÉÔ²Ä¤Î¤È¤­¤Ï£±¥é¥¤¥ó¥Ç¥³¡¼¥É¤Ë¤·¤Æ¤¤¤ë¡£
2131 * ½èÍı¤ò´ÊÊØ¤Ë¤¹¤ë¤¿¤á¡¢¤³¤³¤Ç¤ÏÅ·ÃÏµÕ½ç¤Î»ş¤Ï£±¥é¥¤¥ó¤Î¤ß¤Ë¸ÂÄê¤¹¤ë¡£(¸ÍÅÄ)
2132 */
2133 ASSERT(line_count == 1);
2134 prev_line = (int)(henbairitu *
2135 (float)(pDest->page_info.source_info.length - pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no));
2136 cur_line = (int)(henbairitu *
2137 (float)(pDest->page_info.source_info.length - pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no + line_count));
2138 one_time_fill_line = cur_line - prev_line;
2139 } else {
2140 cur_line = (int)(henbairitu * pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no);
2141 if (pDest->buffer_height > 0) {
2142 prev_line = (int)(henbairitu *
2143 (pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no -
2144 pDest->buffer_height));
2145 } else {
2146 prev_line = (int)(henbairitu *
2147 (pDest->page_info.source_info.fill_line_no -
2148 line_count));
2149 }
2150
2151 one_time_fill_line = cur_line - prev_line;
2152 }
2153 if(one_time_fill_line == 0){
2154 continue; /* Dest¤¬£±¥é¥¤¥ó¤ËËş¤¿¤Ê¤¤»ş¤Ï¥¹¥­¥Ã¥× */
2155 }
2156
2157 /* Image rotatin setting. */
2158 if (!((model_distinct == MODEL_WIDE) &&
2159 (OptionData.pjl_imagedirection
2160 == DI_ENV_VAL_INT_IMAGEDIRECTION_REVERSE))) {
2161 if (( RTIFF_YOKO_KAITEN )||(RTIFF_TATE_KAITEN)) {
2162 flag |= PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_270 ;
2163 }
2164 }
2165 else {
2166 /* 180 degree image rotation by RTIFF. */
2167 if (( RTIFF_YOKO_KAITEN )||(RTIFF_TATE_KAITEN)) {
2168 flag |= PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_90;
2169 }
2170 else {
2171 flag |= PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_180;
2172 }
2173 prev_line = position->h - prev_line - one_time_fill_line;
2174 }
2175
2176 /*
2177 * ¥¯¥ê¥Ã¥×¤Î»ØÄê
2178 */
2179
2180 if ( ( ( clip->sx > position->x ) /* »ÏÅÀsx,sy¤ÎÈÏ°Ï³°*/
2181 || (clip->sy > position->y))
2182 || ((clip->ex < (position->x + position->w)) /* ½ªÅÀex,ey¤ÎÈÏ°Ï³°*/
2183 || (clip->ey < (position->y + position->h)))
2184 ) {
2185 result = pr_rectangle(pDest->prh, PR_ALTCLIP, clip->sx, clip->sy, clip->ex, clip->ey);
2186 if (result != PR_OK) {
2187 PRINTF("rectangle error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
2188 }
2189 }
2190
2191// 2006/09/21 h.funaki depth=4 ¤Î»ş¤Ï¡¢Â¿ÃÍ²èÁü¤ÎÉÁ²è
2192// if (pDest->page_info.source_info.depth == 8) {
2193 if ((pDest->page_info.source_info.depth == 8) ||
2194 (pDest->page_info.source_info.depth == 4)) {
2195
2196 /* ²óÅ¾¤ÎÂĞ±ş position->y + prev_line¢Îposition->x
2197 position->w¢Îone_time_fill_line ¤ÎÆş¤ìÂØ¤¨¤ò¹Ô¤¦ */
2198 if ( ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_90) ||
2199 ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_270 ) ) {
2200
2201 result = pr_func->stretchblt(pDest->prh, flag,
2202 pDest->page_info.source_info.width, line_count,
2203 position->y + prev_line, position->x,
2204 one_time_fill_line, position->w,
2205 pDest->buffer[0], 0);
2206 }
2207 else {
2208 result = pr_func->stretchblt(pDest->prh, flag,
2209 pDest->page_info.source_info.width, line_count,
2210 position->x, position->y + prev_line,
2211 position->w, one_time_fill_line,
2212 pDest->buffer[0], 0);
2213 }
2214
2215 }
2216 else {
2217#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
2218 if (pDest->buffer_height > 0) {
2219 if ( ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_90) ||
2220 ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_270 ) ) {
2221 result = pr_func->stretchblt_index(pDest->prh,
2222 flag|PR_STRBLT_1BPP|PR_STRBLT_INDEX_ON,
2223 pDest->page_info.source_info.width,
2224 line_count,
2225 position->y + prev_line,
2226 position->x,
2227 line_count * 2,
2228 pDest->page_info.source_info.width * 2,
2229 pDest->buffer [0], &mono_index_tbl [0], 0);
2230 }
2231 else {
2232 result = pr_func->stretchblt_index(pDest->prh,
2233 flag|PR_STRBLT_1BPP|PR_STRBLT_INDEX_ON,
2234 pDest->page_info.source_info.width,
2235 line_count,
2236 position->x,
2237 position->y + prev_line,
2238 pDest->page_info.source_info.width * 2,
2239 line_count * 2,
2240 pDest->buffer [0], &mono_index_tbl [0], 0);
2241 }
2242 } else
2243#endif /* USE_MP_TIFF */
2244 /* ²óÅ¾¤ÎÂĞ±ş position->y + prev_line¢Îposition->x
2245 position->w¢Îone_time_fill_line ¤ÎÆş¤ìÂØ¤¨¤ò¹Ô¤¦ */
2246 if ( ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_90) ||
2247 ((flag & PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_MASK) == PR_IMAGE_ROTATE_270 ) ) {
2248 result = pr_func->stretchblt_index(pDest->prh, flag|PR_STRBLT_1BPP|PR_STRBLT_INDEX_ON ,
2249 pDest->page_info.source_info.width, line_count,
2250 position->y + prev_line, position->x,
2251 one_time_fill_line, position->w,
2252 pDest->buffer [0], &mono_index_tbl [0], 0);
2253 }
2254 else {
2255
2256 result = pr_func->stretchblt_index(pDest->prh, flag|PR_STRBLT_1BPP|PR_STRBLT_INDEX_ON ,
2257 pDest->page_info.source_info.width, line_count,
2258 position->x, position->y + prev_line,
2259 position->w, one_time_fill_line,
2260 pDest->buffer [0], &mono_index_tbl [0], 0);
2261 }
2262 }
2263 if (result != PR_OK) {
2264 PRINTF("stretchblt error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
2265 }
2266 result = pr_resetclip(pDest->prh);
2267 if (result != PR_OK) {
2268 PRINTF("resetclip error %d\n", pr_func->get_errorcode(pDest->prh));
2269 }
2270 position++;
2271 clip++;
2272 }
2273#ifdef DEBUG_LINE
2274 PRINTF("lineno %d->%d \n", pDest->page_info.destnation_info.offset, pDest->page_info.destnation_info.offset+line_count);
2275#endif /* DEBUG_LINE */
2276 return ;
2277}
