2279#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
2280void prcall_write_end_page_image_draw(prif_dest_ptr pDest)
2281#else
2282void prcall_write_end_page_image_draw(prif_dest_ptr pDest, int output_mode)
2283#endif
2284{
2285
2286 prfunc_call_t *pr_func;
2287 unsigned long status;
2288 int result;
2289 unsigned long jobreset;
2290 DBG_MSG_PRCALL("prcall_write_end_page_image_draw\n");
2291
2292 status = prcall_get_internal_status();
2293 /*
2294 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³«»ÏÃæ¤Î¤ß½èÍı¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
2295 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³«»Ï¤¬OFF¤Î¾ì¹ç¤Ï¡¢¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥È¤Ş¤¿¤Ï¥¨¥é¡¼¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥ÈÈ¯À¸
2296 */
2297
2298 if (status & PRCALL_STATUS_JOBSTART) {
2299 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
2300 result = pr_func->bandend(pDest->prh);
2301 if (result != PR_OK) {
2302 jobreset = prcall_check_job_reset();
2303 if (jobreset != 0) {
2304 __ERROR("PRCALL_STATUS_JOBRESET");
2305 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_JOBRESET);
2306 }
2307 else {
2308 __ERROR("PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_LIBRARY");
2309 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_LIBRARY);
2310 }
2311 }
2312 else {
2313#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
2314 /* FREE SIZE¤Î»ş¤Ï¡¢¶¯À©°õºş¤ò¹Ô¤¦ */
2315 if( CheckFreeSize(0) || (CheckFreeSize(1)) ) {
2316 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, 4);
2317 }
2318 else {
2319 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, 0);
2320 }
2321#else
2322 if(output_mode == PRINT_OK) {
2323 long freesize_normal = CheckFreeSize(1);
2324 long freesize_bypass = CheckFreeSize(0);
2325
2326 if((freesize_normal == 1) || (freesize_bypass == 1)) {
2327 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, PR_PAPERFEED_FORCE);
2328 }
2329 else {
2330 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, PR_PAPERFEED_NORMAL);
2331 }
2332 } else {
2333 /* Ignore images need not to draw on the way of preview process. */
2334 pr_func->pageend(pDest->prh, PR_PAPERFEED_NOTPRINT);
2335 }
2336#endif
2337 }
2338
2339 }
2340
2341 return;
2342}
2343void prcall_write_end_job(void)
2344{
2345 prfunc_call_t *pr_func;
2346 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
2347 unsigned long status;
2348
2349#ifdef USE_USERFORM
2350 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_MAIN);
2351#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
2352 pDest = (prif_dest_ptr)(prcall_ext_info_ptr->dest);
2353#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
2354 status = prcall_get_internal_status();
2355 pr_func = (prfunc_call_t *)pDest->pr_func;
2356 /*
2357 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³«»ÏÃæ¤Î¤ß½èÍı¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
2358 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö³«»Ï¤¬OFF¤Î¾ì¹ç¤Ï¡¢¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥È¤Ş¤¿¤Ï¥¨¥é¡¼¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥ê¥»¥Ã¥ÈÈ¯À¸
2359 */
2360 if (status & PRCALL_STATUS_JOBSTART) {
2361
2362 /* Set job cancel flags. */
2363 if (aspara.jobreset == TRUE) {
2364 /* Job was canceled by panel(GPS). */
2365 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = TRUE;
2366 }
2367#ifndef USE_MP_TIFF
2368 /* Error occurs when calling the "gpsPlotCancelLater"
2369 by the MediaPrintTIFF. */
2370 else {
2371 if ((RtiffIF.SummaryON == RTIFF_PRINT_ERROR) &&
2372 (prcall_ext_info.job_reseted == TRUE)) {
2373 /* If print error log after the job canceled by PDL. */
2374 aspara.jobreset = TRUE;
2375 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = FALSE;
2376 }
2377 }
2378#endif
2379
2380 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_JOBEND);
2381 pr_func->jobend(pDest->prh);
2382
2383 }
2384 else {
2385 /* Set job cancel flags. */
2386 /* NOTICE: When you pushed reset button after PDL had canceled job, */
2387 /* this process regard that job was canceled by PDL. */
2388 if (prcall_ext_info.job_reseted == TRUE) {
2389 /* Job was canceled by PDL. */
2390#ifndef USE_MP_TIFF
2391 int error_cnt;
2392
2393 /* Return value is curent error count + 1. */
2394 error_cnt = get_ep_no() - 1;
2395 if (!(RtiffIF.ErrPrint && (error_cnt > 0))) {
2396 /* If not print Error Log. */
2397 aspara.jobreset = TRUE;
2398 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = FALSE;
2399 }
2400#else
2401 aspara.jobreset = TRUE;
2402 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = TRUE;
2403#endif
2404 } else if (aspara.jobreset == TRUE) {
2405 /* Job was canceled by panel(GPS). */
2406 prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = TRUE;
2407 } else {
2408 /* Inhibit QAC warning. */
2409 ;
2410 }
2411
2412 DBG_MSG_INTERNAL_STATUS("pr_func->abort");
2413 pr_func->abort(pDest->prh);
2414
2415 PRINTF("prcall_write_end_job no jobstart\n");
2416 }
2417
2418#ifdef USE_TIME_STAT
2419 {
2420 unsigned int ptime ;
2421
2422 ptime = get_jobtime();
2423
2424 /* 00'00"00 format */
2425 PRINTF("JOB: %d'%d\"%d (%d.%dPPM)\r\n",
2426 ptime / (60 * 100), ptime % (60 * 100) / 100, ptime % 100,
2427 (int)(60.0 * pDest->page_info.no * 100 / ptime),
2428 (int)(60.0 * pDest->page_info.no * 100 / ptime * 100) % 100);
2429 }
2430#endif
2431 return;
2432
2433
2434}
2435/*
2436 * ¥¸¥ç¥Ö¤ò½ªÎ»ÄÌÃÎ¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
2437 */
2438void prcall_jobend(void)
2439{
2440
2441 DBG_MSG_PRCALL("prcall_jobend\n");
2442 di_close_host();
2443#ifdef USE_DI_V2
2444 di_close_ohost();
2445#endif
2446 di_notify_msg( DI_NOTIFYMSG_JOBEND, 0 ); /* DI¤Ë¡¢½ªÎ»¤òÄÌÃÎ¤¹¤ë */
2447
2448}

2450static void set_prdevinfo( dev_info_t *di_info, pr_dev_info_t *pr_info )
2451{
2452 unsigned char info_bandsize_str[DI_MAX_VALUE_LEN];
2453 char appinfo_str[DI_MAX_VALUE_LEN];
2454 int ret_di_get_appinfo;
2455
2456 if( !di_info || !pr_info )
2457 return;
2458
2459 /* £°¤Ç½é´ü²½¤·¤Æ¤ª¤¯ */
2460 MEMZERO( pr_info, sizeof(pr_dev_info_t) );
2461
2462 /* ¥Ç¥£¥¶¥­¥ã¥Ã¥·¥å¤Ï¼«Á°¤ÎÃÍ¤ò»ÈÍÑ¤¹¤ë¤è¤¦¤ËÊÑ¹¹ */
2463
2464 pr_info->resonum = di_info->resonum;
2465 pr_info->reso_set = (pr_resolution_info_t *)di_info->reso_set;
2466
2467 pr_info->dither_info = (pr_dit_info_t *)di_info->dither_info;
2468 pr_info->gamma_info = di_info->gamma_info;
2469 pr_info->font_address = di_info->font_address;
2470 pr_info->font_size = di_info->font_size;
2471#ifdef GPS
2472 if (di_info->nplane == 1) /* ¥â¥Î¥¯¥íµ¡ */
2473 pr_info->dither_cache = 128*1024; /* 128K */
2474 else
2475 pr_info->dither_cache = 500*1024; /* 500K */
2476#else /* Unix or Windows */
2477 pr_info->dither_cache = 300*1024; /* 300K */
2478#endif /* GPS */
2479
2480 ret_di_get_appinfo = di_get_appinfo("bandsize", "DI", &info_bandsize_str[0]);
2481 if (ret_di_get_appinfo == DI_PINI_OK) {
2482 pr_info->bandsize = atoi(&info_bandsize_str[0]);
2483 pr_info->band_4C_thresh = pr_info->bandsize * 100 * 1024;
2484 } else {
2485 ret_di_get_appinfo = di_get_appinfo("info_bandsize", "RTIFF", &info_bandsize_str[0]);
2486 if (ret_di_get_appinfo == DI_PINI_OK) {
2487 pr_info->bandsize = atoi(&info_bandsize_str[0]);
2488 } else {
2489 pr_info->bandsize = 20;
2490 }
2491 }
2492 pr_info->ndit = di_info->ndit;
2493 pr_info->nplane = di_info->nplane;
2494 pr_info->bg_startp = di_info->bg_startp;
2495 pr_info->bg_slant = di_info->bg_slant;
2496 pr_info->ucr_startp = di_info->ucr_startp;
2497 pr_info->ucr_slant = di_info->ucr_slant;
2498 pr_info->soft_tsave = di_info->soft_tsave;
2499 pr_info->tsave_ratio = di_info->tsave_ratio;
2500 pr_info->toner_limit = di_info->toner_limit;
2501#ifdef USE_EXTEND_TONERSAVING

2617/*
2618 * µ¡Ç½¡§°õºş¥Ñ¥é¥á¡¼¥¿¤Î½é´ü²½
2619 * ÆâÉôÀßÄê¤µ¤ì¤Æ¤¤¤ë½é´ü²½¥Ñ¥é¥á¡¼¥¿¤ò°õºş»ş¥Ñ¥é¥á¡¼¥¿¤ËÈ¿±Ç¤µ¤»¤ë¡£
2620 */
2621prif_dest_ptr prcall_write_init_prif(void)
2622{
2623
2624 int pos_type;
2625 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
2626 int scaling_factor;
2627 double d_scaling_factor;
2628
2629 /* Create module interface object, fill in method pointers */
2630#ifdef USE_USERFORM
2631 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_MAIN);
2632#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
2633 pDest = (prif_dest_ptr)(prcall_ext_info_ptr->dest);
2634#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
2635
2636 /*
2637 * °õºş´ØÏ¢¾ğÊóÀßÄê ¡Ê³ÈÂç¡¢²óÅ¾¡¢²òÁüÅÙ¡Ë
2638 */
2639
2640 if ((prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_zoom > MODE_ZOOM_MAX)
2641 || (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_zoom == 0))
2642 pDest->page_info.zoom = 1;
2643 else
2644 pDest->page_info.zoom = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_zoom;
2645 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_rotate > MODE_ROTATE_MAX)
2646 pDest->page_info.rotate = 0;
2647 else
2648 pDest->page_info.rotate = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_rotate;
2649
2650 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_dpix != 0)
2651 pDest->page_info.dpix = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_dpix;
2652 else
2653 pDest->page_info.dpix = 600;
2654
2655 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_dpiy != 0)
2656 pDest->page_info.dpiy = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_dpiy;
2657 else
2658 pDest->page_info.dpiy = 600;
2659
2660 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_depth != 0)
2661 pDest->page_info.depth = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_depth;
2662 else
2663 pDest->page_info.depth = 1; /* USE 1bit depth */
2664
2665 ASSERT(prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_plane != 0);
2666 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_plane != 0)
2667 pDest->page_info.plane = prcall_ext_info_ptr->mode_plane;
2668
2669 /*
2670 * ½é´ü¾õÂÖ¤Î¥Ú¡¼¥¸¾ğÊó¤Ï¥Ú¡¼¥¸¤Î¥µ¥¤¥º¡¢¥Ç¥¹¥È¥Í¡¼¥·¥ç¥ó¤Î¥µ¥¤¥º¤òÀßÄê
2671 * ¥Ç¥¹¥È¥Í¡¼¥·¥ç¥ó¤Î¥µ¥¤¥º¤Ï¡¢½é´üÃÍ¤ÏÍÑ»æ¤Î¥µ¥¤¥º¤ÈÆ±¤¸¤Ë¤¹¤ë¡£
2672 * ¥½¡¼¥¹¤Î¥µ¥¤¥º¤Ë¤Ä¤¤¤Æ¤Ï¡¢¥Ç¥³¡¼¥ÉÂ¦¤Ç¥½¡¼¥¹¤Î¥µ¥¤¥º¤òÀßÄê¤¹¤ë¡£
2673 */
2674 d_scaling_factor = (double)pDest->page_info.dpiy / 600.0 ;
2675
2676 /* Page size and page margin setting */
2677 if ( RtiffIF.RtiffON ) {
2678 unsigned long paper_w, paper_h;
2679 unsigned long paper_marginx, paper_marginy;
2680 long page_w, page_h;
2681 long page_offx, page_offy;
2682 int free_marginx, free_marginy;
2683 int leftsp, rightsp, uppsp, lowsp;
2684 int fRot180;
2685 int fBackSide;
2686 extern struct optionPara OptionData;
2687
2688 paper_w = prcall_ext_info_ptr->width * d_scaling_factor;
2689 paper_h = prcall_ext_info_ptr->length * d_scaling_factor;
2690 paper_marginx = prcall_ext_info_ptr->marginX * d_scaling_factor;
2691 paper_marginy = prcall_ext_info_ptr->marginY * d_scaling_factor;
2692
2693 leftsp = OptionData.leftspace;
2694 rightsp = OptionData.rightspace;
2695 uppsp = OptionData.upperspace;
2696 lowsp = OptionData.lowerspace;
2697
2698 free_marginx = 0;
2699 free_marginy = 0;
2700
2701 fRot180 = (model_distinct == MODEL_WIDE) &&
2702 (OptionData.pjl_imagedirection
2703 == DI_ENV_VAL_INT_IMAGEDIRECTION_REVERSE);
2704
2705 fBackSide = (RtiffIF.Ctr_bothside == PR_FACE_DPX1ST) &&
2706 (pDest->env_job.paper_code == pDest->env_page.paper_code) &&
2707 (pDest->env_job.paper_type == pDest->env_page.paper_type);
2708
2709 if ( !RtiffIF.MaxArea ) {
2710 if (leftsp < 0) {
2711 leftsp = 0;
2712 }
2713 if (rightsp < 0) {
2714 rightsp = 0;
2715 }
2716 if (uppsp < 0) {
2717 uppsp = 0;
2718 }
2719 if (lowsp < 0) {
2720 lowsp = 0;
2721 }
2722
2723 /* Delete margin from printing area when paper size is free. */
2724 if (IS_PAPER_FREE(RtiffIF.Ptype) ||
2725 IS_PAPER_FREE_TESASI(RtiffIF.Ptype) ||
2726 ((RtiffIF.Ptype >= PAPER_S1) && (RtiffIF.Ptype <= PAPER_S9))) {
2727 free_marginx = ROLL_FREE_MARGINX * d_scaling_factor;
2728 free_marginy = ROLL_FREE_MARGINY * d_scaling_factor;
2729 }
2730 }
2731 if ( ( RTIFF_YOKO_KAITEN ) || ( RTIFF_TATE_KAITEN ) ) {
2732 page_w = paper_w - (lowsp + uppsp + free_marginy);
2733 page_h = paper_h - (rightsp + leftsp + free_marginx);
2734
2735 if (!fRot180) {
2736 /* 270 degree image rotation */
2737 if (!fBackSide) {
2738 page_offx = paper_marginx + uppsp;
2739 page_offy = paper_marginy + rightsp;
2740 }
2741 else {
2742 if (RtiffIF.Bothside == SIDE_DUPLEX) {
2743 page_offx = paper_marginx + uppsp;
2744 page_offy = paper_marginy + leftsp;
2745 }
2746 else {
2747 page_offx = paper_marginx + lowsp;
2748 page_offy = paper_marginy + rightsp;
2749 }
2750 }
2751 }
2752 else {
2753 /* 90 degree image rotation */
2754 page_offx = paper_marginx + lowsp;
2755 page_offy = paper_marginy + leftsp;
2756 }
2757 }
2758 else {
2759 page_w = paper_w - (rightsp + leftsp + free_marginx);
2760 page_h = paper_h - (lowsp + uppsp + free_marginy);
2761
2762 if (!fRot180) {
2763 /* Image no rotation */
2764 if (!fBackSide) {
2765 page_offx = paper_marginx + leftsp;
2766 page_offy = paper_marginy + uppsp;
2767 }
2768 else {
2769 if (RtiffIF.Bothside == SIDE_DUPLEX) {
2770 page_offx = paper_marginx + rightsp;
2771 page_offy = paper_marginy + uppsp;
2772 }
2773 else {
2774 page_offx = paper_marginx + leftsp;
2775 page_offy = paper_marginy + lowsp;
2776 }
2777 }
2778 }
2779 else {
2780 /* 180 degree image rotation */
2781 page_offx = paper_marginx + rightsp;
2782 page_offy = paper_marginy + lowsp;
2783 }
2784 }
2785 if (page_w < 0) {
2786 pDest->page_info.width = 0;
2787 }
2788 else {
2789 pDest->page_info.width = page_w;
2790 }
2791 if (page_h < 0) {
2792 pDest->page_info.height = 0;
2793 }
2794 else {
2795 pDest->page_info.height = page_h;
2796 }
2797 pDest->page_info.offsetX = page_offx;
2798 pDest->page_info.offsetY = page_offy;
2799
2800 if (!RtiffIF.MaxArea) {
2801 if (!fBackSide) {
2802 if (OptionData.leftspace < 0) {
2803 RtiffIF.OffsetX += OptionData.leftspace ;
2804 }
2805 if (OptionData.upperspace < 0) {
2806 RtiffIF.OffsetY += OptionData.upperspace ;
2807 }
2808 }
2809 else {
2810 if (RtiffIF.Bothside == SIDE_DUPLEX) {
2811 if (OptionData.rightspace < 0) {
2812 RtiffIF.OffsetX += OptionData.rightspace ;
2813 }
2814 if (OptionData.upperspace < 0) {
2815 RtiffIF.OffsetY += OptionData.upperspace ;
2816 }
2817 }
2818 else {
2819 if (OptionData.leftspace < 0) {
2820 RtiffIF.OffsetX += OptionData.leftspace ;
2821 }
2822 if (OptionData.lowerspace < 0) {
2823 RtiffIF.OffsetY += OptionData.lowerspace ;
2824 }
2825 }
2826 }
2827 }
2828
2829 }
2830 else {
2831 pDest->page_info.width = (double)prcall_ext_info_ptr->width * d_scaling_factor;
2832 pDest->page_info.height = (double)prcall_ext_info_ptr->length * d_scaling_factor;
2833 pDest->page_info.offsetX = (double)prcall_ext_info_ptr->marginX * d_scaling_factor;
2834 pDest->page_info.offsetY = (double)prcall_ext_info_ptr->marginY * d_scaling_factor;
2835 }
2836
2837#if 0
2838printf( "---------------------------------------\n" ) ;
2839printf( " pDest->page_info.width:%d\n", pDest->page_info.width ) ;
2840printf( " pDest->page_info.height:%d\n", pDest->page_info.height ) ;
2841printf( " pDest->page_info.offsetX:%d\n", pDest->page_info.offsetX ) ;
2842printf( " pDest->page_info.offsetY:%d\n", pDest->page_info.offsetY ) ;
2843printf( "---------------------------------------\n" ) ;
2844#endif
2845
2846 if (di_get_trayinfo(&di_tinfo) != 0) { /* ¥È¥ì¥¤¾ğÊó¼èÆÀ */
2847 ASSERT(0);
2848 }
2849#ifdef USE_STAPLE_POS_LOCATION
2850 /*
2851 * ¥Ú¡¼¥¸¤´¤È¤ÎÍÑ»æ¥µ¥¤¥º¾ğÊó¤Ë¤è¤ê¡¢¥¹¥Æ¡¼¥×¥ë»ş¤Î²óÅ¾À©¸æ¤ò¹Ô¤¦¾ğÊó¤òÀßÄê¤¹¤ë¡£
2852 * ¸½¾õ¤Ç¤Ï¡¢¥Ï¡¼¥É¤Ç90ÅÙ¡¢270ÅÙ²óÅ¾²ÄÇ½¤Êµ¡¼ï¤Ç¤Ï¡¢¤³¤Î¾ğÊó¤Ï»ÈÍÑ¤·¤Ê¤¤
2853 */
2854 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->staple_pos_location != 0)
2855 pDest->page_info.staple_rotate_info = prcall_ext_info_ptr->staple_pos_rotate_container + prcall_ext_info_ptr->staple_pos_location;
2856 else
2857 pDest->page_info.staple_rotate_info = NULL;
2858#ifdef DEBUG_STAPLE_POS_LOCATION
2859 {
2860 const rotate_info_t *rotate_pos;
2861
2862 rotate_pos = pDest->page_info.staple_rotate_info;
2863 if (rotate_pos != NULL) {
2864 PRINTF("staple pos1 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[0]);
2865 PRINTF("staple pos2 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[1]);
2866 PRINTF("staple pos3 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[2]);
2867 PRINTF("staple pos4 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[3]);
2868 PRINTF("staple pos5 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[4]);
2869 PRINTF("staple pos6 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[5]);
2870 PRINTF("staple pos7 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[6]);
2871 PRINTF("staple pos8 %d\n", rotate_pos->staple_pos[7]);
2872 }
2873 }
2874#endif /* DEBUG_STAPLE_POS_LOCATION */
2875
2876#endif
2877
2878 /*
2879 * ÍÑ»æ¾ğÊó¤ÎÀßÄê¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£
2880 */
2881 pDest->page_info.paper.flag = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.flag;
2882 pDest->page_info.paper.tray_id = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.tray_id;
2883 pDest->page_info.paper.id = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.id;
2884 pDest->page_info.paper.kind = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.kind;
2885 pDest->page_info.paper.length = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.length;
2886 pDest->page_info.paper.width = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.width;
2887 pDest->page_info.paper.direction = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.direction;
2888#ifdef DEBUG_PAPER_DETAIL_INFORMATION
2889 PRINTF("paper.flag 0x%04xd\n", pDest->page_info.paper.flag);
2890 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_TRAY_ID) {
2891 PRINTF("tray_id %02d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.tray_id);
2892 }
2893 PRINTF("id %02d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.id);
2894 PRINTF("kind 0x%02x\n", pDest->page_info.paper.kind);
2895 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_SIZE) {
2896 PRINTF("length %d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.length);
2897 PRINTF("width %d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.width);
2898 }
2899 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_DIRECTION) {
2900 PRINTF("direction %d\n", pDest->page_info.paper.direction);
2901 }
2902#endif /* DEBUG_STAPLE_POS_LOCATION */
2903
2904 pDest->page_info.image_profile = prcall_ext_info_ptr->image_profile;
2905 pDest->page_info.graphics_profile = prcall_ext_info_ptr->graphics_profile;
2906 pDest->page_info.text_profile = prcall_ext_info_ptr->text_profile;
2907 pDest->page_info.line_profile = prcall_ext_info_ptr->line_profile;
2908
2909 return pDest; /* ½é´ü²½À®¸ù */
2910
2911}
2912/*
2913 * ¥Ú¡¼¥¸Ëè¤Ë¤«¤ï¤ë¾ğÊó¤òÀßÄê¤¹¤ë
2914 */
2915
2916/*
2917 * »ØÄê¤·¤¿²òÁüÅÙ¤Î¾ğÊó¤ò¼èÆÀ¤¹¤ë
2918 * ÆşÎÏ : ²òÁüÅÙ¥Ó¥Ã¥È¿¼¤µ¤Î¥Æ¡¼¥Ö¥ë
2919 * ¥Æ¡¼¥Ö¥ë¤Î¸Ä¿ô
2920 * ½ĞÎÏ °õºşÉÊ¼Á¤ËÂĞ¤¹¤ë²òÁüÅÙ¥Æ¡¼¥Ö¥ë¤Ø¤Î¥İ¥¤¥ó¥¿
2921 * Éüµ¢¾ğÊó 0:Àµ¾ï -1:³ºÅö¤¹¤ë¾ğÊó¤¬Ìµ¤¤
2922 */
2923int prsub_get_reso_set(
2924 resolution_info_t *reso_set,
2925 int reso_num,
2926 int mode,
2927 resolution_info_t **reso_ptr)
2928{
2929#ifdef USE_IMAQ
2930 int i;
2931 int max = 0;
2932 int reso_bit;
2933 int found = 0;
2934
2935 unsigned char kind;
2936 resolution_info_t *tmp_reso_set;
2937
2938 if (!reso_set || !reso_ptr || !reso_num){
2939 return -1;
2940 }
2941 tmp_reso_set = reso_set;
2942 kind = prcall_ext_info_ptr->paper.kind;
2943#ifdef DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY
2944 PRINTF(" prsub_get_reso_set param\n");
2945 PRINTF(" kind %d,reso_num %d, mode %d\n", kind, reso_num, mode);
2946
2947#endif /* DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY */
2948 if (kind == 0xff) {
2949 /*
2950 * Ëü¤¬°ì¤³¤³¤Ş¤Ç¤Î´Ö¤Ë»æ¼ï¤¬·èÄê¤·¤Æ¤¤¤Ê¤«¤Ã¤¿¤é
2951 * ÉáÄÌ»æ¡¿ºÆÀ¸»æ¤òÀßÄê¤¹¤ë¡£
2952 */
2953 __ERROR("prsub_get_reso_set NO PAPER SELECT\n");
2954 kind = DI_PAPER_AUTO;
2955 }
2956 for (i = 0; i < reso_num; i++, tmp_reso_set++) {
2957#ifdef DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY
2958 PRINTF("SEARCH PRINT QUALITY %d\n", i + 1);
2959 PRINTF(" ->x %d\n", tmp_reso_set->x);
2960 PRINTF(" ->y %d\n", tmp_reso_set->y);
2961 PRINTF(" ->bit %d\n", tmp_reso_set->bit);
2962 PRINTF(" ->prt_mode %d\n", tmp_reso_set->prt_mode);
2963 PRINTF(" ->paper %d\n", tmp_reso_set->paper);
2964#endif /* DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY */

2975#endif /* DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY */

2983 found = 1;

2985 }

2988 if(reso_bit >= max){
2989 *reso_ptr = tmp_reso_set;
2990 max = reso_bit;
2991 found = 1;
2992 }
2993 }
2994 }
2995

2997 if ((i == reso_num) && (found == 0)) {

3000 * »æ¼ï¤¬°ì¼ïÎà¤·¤«¤Ê¤¤¤¿¤á¡¢»ØÄê¤µ¤ì¤¿»æ¼ï¤Î¾ò·ï¤¬¸«¤Ä¤«¤é¤Ê¤«¤Ã¤¿¡£
3001 */
3002#ifdef DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY
3003 PRINTF("NO SEARCH PRINT QUALITY next\n");
3004#endif /* DEBUG_OPTION_PRINT_QUALITY */
3005 kind = reso_set->paper; /* ÀèÆ¬¤Î»æ¼ï¤ÈÆ±¤¸»æ¼ï¤Ç¸¡º÷¤ò¹Ô¤¦¡£ */

3020 */

3025 *reso_ptr = tmp_reso_set;

3030 if(reso_bit >= max){

3071 continue;
3072 }

3074 if(reso_bit >= max){
3075 *reso_ptr = tmp_reso_set;
3076 max = reso_bit;
3077 }
3078 }
3079 }
3080#endif /* USE_IMAQ */
3081 return 0;

3083
3084void prsub_get_colorprofile(unsigned char kind, unsigned long *vividness,
3085 unsigned long *gradation, unsigned long *text)
3086{
3087 int i, j, k;
3088 int di_result = DI_PINI_ERROR;
3089 char pini_key[16];
3090 char pini_parameter[32];
3091 char workarea[16];
3092 long pini_kind;
3093
3094 if((vividness == NULL) || (gradation == NULL) || (text ==NULL)){
3095 return;
3096 }
3097
3098 for(i = 1; ; i++){
3099
3100 sprintf(pini_key, "colorprofile%d", i);
3101 di_result = di_get_appinfo(pini_key,"IDP",&pini_parameter[0]);
3102
3103 if(di_result != DI_PINI_OK){
3104 break;
3105 }
3106
3107 /* Pick paper kind. */
3108 for(j = 0, k = 0; pini_parameter[k] != ',' ; j++, k++){
3109 workarea[j] = pini_parameter[k];
3110 }
3111 workarea[j] = '\0';
3112 pini_kind = strtol(workarea, NULL, 16);
3113 k++;
3114
3115 if((pini_kind == kind) || (i == 1)){
3116 /* Pick vividness. */
3117 for(j = 0; pini_parameter[k] != ',' ; j++, k++){
3118 workarea[j] = pini_parameter[k];
3119 }
3120 workarea[j] = '\0';
3121 *vividness = strtol(workarea, NULL, 16);
3122 k++;
3123
3124 /* Pick gradation. */
3125 for(j = 0; pini_parameter[k] != ',' ; j++, k++){
3126 workarea[j] = pini_parameter[k];
3127 }
3128 workarea[j] = '\0';
3129 *gradation = strtol(workarea, NULL, 16);
3130 k++;
3131
3132 /* Pick text. */
3133 for(j = 0; pini_parameter[k] != '\0' ; j++, k++){
3134 workarea[j] = pini_parameter[k];
3135 }
3136 workarea[j] = '\0';
3137 *text = strtol(workarea, NULL, 16);
3138
3139 if(pini_kind == kind){
3140 break;
3141 }
3142 }
3143 }
3144}

3404#endif

3406

3409static int prsub_init(void)
3410{
3411
3412 prif_dest_ptr pDest;

3668int prcall_init(int function)
3669{

3673

3727#endif /* NETBSD */

3730 /*
3731 * ¥á¥â¥ê¥¨¥é¡¼¤òÀßÄê
3732 */

3734 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_ERROR_MEMORY);
3735 return -1;
3736 }
3737 /*
3738 * alloc PDL work memory
3739 */
3740 prcall_ext_info_ptr->total_memory_size = malloc_memory_size;
3741
3742 /*
3743 * set spool size 35% of total memory
3744 */
3745 res = di_get_bitswinfo(DI_BIT_SW_007, &bitsw);
3746 if (res == 0) {
3747 gipaFlag = check_HW_acceleration((unsigned char)bitsw);
3748 }
3749 else {
3750 gipaFlag = __ADVANCED_FUNC_RESULT_OFF;
3751 }
3752 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr == NULL) {
3753 /* QAC */
3754 return -1;
3755 }
3756
3757 if (gipaFlag == __ADVANCED_FUNC_RESULT_ON) {
3758 pr_used_spool_size = prcall_ext_info_ptr->pr_used_spools_size
3759 = (((malloc_memory_size - GIPA_MEMORY_SIZE) * 7) / 20) / 1024;
3760 }
3761 else {
3762 pr_used_spool_size = prcall_ext_info_ptr->pr_used_spools_size
3763 = ((malloc_memory_size * 7) / 20) / 1024;
3764 }
3765
3766 data_addr = (unsigned char *)di_memory_alloc(malloc_memory_size);
3767 /*
3768 * data_addr¤¬¼¨¤¹ÎÎ°è¤òº£¸å¤Îºî¶È¥¨¥ê¥¢¤È¤·¡¢¥á¥â¥ê´ÉÍı¤ò¹Ô¤¦

3772 /* 2008/12/16 h.funaki PRpf VerUp¤ËÈ¼¤¦½¤Àµ */
3773// mmInit(prcall_ext_info_ptr->mmh, data_addr, malloc_memory_size);

3791 if (result == 0) {

3800

3802

3807 pDest->destnation_type = PRCALL_DEST_TYPE_MAIN; /* pDest¤Î¼ïÊÌ¤òmain¤Ë¤¹¤ë */

3812 */
3813 pDest = (prif_dest_ptr)prcall_malloc_tiffwork(sizeof(prif_dest_t));
3814 if (pDest != NULL) {
3815 MEMZERO(pDest, sizeof(prif_dest_t)); /* ¥Ú¡¼¥¸¾ğÊó½é´ü²½ */
3816 pDest->destnation_type = PRCALL_DEST_TYPE_SUB; /* pDest¤Î¼ïÊÌ¤òSUB¤Ë¤¹¤ë */
3817 prcall_ext_info_ptr->dest [1] = pDest;
3818
3819 }
3820#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
3821 prcall_ext_info_ptr->dest = pDest;
3822#endif /* USE_USERFORM */

3825 * ¥È¥ì¥¤¾ğÊó¤Î¼èÆÀ
3826 * 1:¶¯À©¼èÆÀ¤ò»ØÄê¤¹¤ë
3827 */

3839 = prcall_AvailAlloc_tiffwork();
3840
3841 PRINTF("AlMS=%lu,", malloc_memory_size);
3842 PRINTF("PrMS=%lu,", prcall_ext_info_ptr->pr_used_memory_size);
3843 PRINTF("SpMS=%lu,", prcall_ext_info_ptr->pr_used_spools_size
3844 * 1024);
3845
3846 if (prsub_init() < 0) {
3847 di_memory_free((char *)data_addr);
3848 di_term();

3850 }
3851 for (i = 0; i < devinfo.resonum; i++) {
3852 PRINTF("%dx%dx%d-%d-%d-%d,", devinfo.reso_set[i].x,
3853 devinfo.reso_set[i].y,

3867 return 0;
3868 }

3873 }

3875#ifdef _DEBUG

3877#endif

3880 return -1;
3881}
3882/* ÆÃÊÌ½èÍı ********************************************************************/
3883int Speciallyfunction ; /* ÆÃÊÌ½èÍı */
3884#define SPECIALLYFUNCTION_NONE 0 /* ¤Ê¤· */
3885#define SPECIALLYFUNCTION_PROGENTRY 1 /* ¥×¥í¥°¥é¥àÅĞÏ¿ */
3886#define SPECIALLYFUNCTION_PROGDELETE 2 /* ¥×¥í¥°¥é¥àºï½ü */
3887#define SPECIALLYFUNCTION_INTRAY 3 /* µë»æ¥È¥ì¥¤ */
3888#define SPECIALLYFUNCTION_TESTPRINT_SUMMARY 11 /* ¥Æ¥¹¥È°õºş(°õºş¾ò·ï) */
3889#define SPECIALLYFUNCTION_TESTPRINT_PROGRAM 12 /* ¥Æ¥¹¥È°õºş(¥×¥í¥°¥é¥à°ìÍ÷°õºş) */
3890/***********************************************************************************/
3891/*
3892 * µ¡Ç½¡§EOI¤Î¼¡¤Î¥Ğ¥¤¥È¤ò¼èÆÀ¤·¡¢¥·¥¹¥Æ¥à¤«¤é¤ÎÍ×µá¤Ë½¾¤Ã¤Æ½èÍı¤ò¹Ô¤¦
3893
3894 */
3895
3896int prcall_continue(void)
3897{
3898
3899 int result;
3900 int ret;
3901
3902 result = 0; /* Àµ¾ï½ªÎ» ¼¡¤ÎJPEG¤ò¥Ç¥³¡¼¥É²ÄÇ½ */
3903 DBG_MSG_PRCALL("prcall_continue\n");
3904 /*
3905 * ¥Ç¡¼¥¿ÂÔ¤Á¤Î¥¹¥Æ¡¼¥¿¥¹¤ËÀßÄê
3906 */
3907 prcall_set_internal_status(PRCALL_STATUS_DATA_WAIT);
3908
3909 /* ÆÃÊÌ½èÍı¤Î½é´ü²½ */
3910 Speciallyfunction = 0 ;
3911
3912 switch( di_get_request() ) {
3913
3914 case DI_REQ_EXIT:
3915 case DI_REQ_TERM :
3916
3917 /* ¥¤¥ó¥¿¥×¥ê¥¿½ªÎ»Í×µá */
3918 result = -1; /* ½ªÎ»¤¹¤ë */
3919 break;
3920 case DI_REQ_PROCESS:
3921 /* ÄÌ¾ï°õºşÍ×µá */
3922 aspara.jobreset = prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = FALSE;
3923#ifdef DEBUG
3924 PRINTF("REQ_PROCESS aspara.not_joblang %d\n", aspara.not_joblang);
3925#endif
3926
3927 /* ¥Æ¥¹¥È°õºş¤Î¥Á¥§¥Ã¥¯ */
3928 switch (aspara.testprint ) {
3929 case DI_INTERP_TESTPRINT_SUMMARY :
3930 Speciallyfunction = SPECIALLYFUNCTION_TESTPRINT_SUMMARY ;
3931// aspara.testprint = 0 ;
3932 break ;
3933 case DI_INTERP_TESTPRINT_PROGRAM :
3934 Speciallyfunction = SPECIALLYFUNCTION_TESTPRINT_PROGRAM ;
3935// aspara.testprint = 0 ;
3936 break ;
3937 default :
3938 Speciallyfunction = SPECIALLYFUNCTION_NONE ;
3939// aspara.testprint = 0
3940
3941
3942 break ;
3943 }
3944
3945 break;
3946 case DI_REQ_CANCEL:
3947 /* ¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥­¥ã¥ó¥»¥ëÍ×µá */
3948 aspara.jobreset = prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = TRUE;
3949#ifdef DEBUG_JOBREST
3950 PRINTF("prcall_continue DI_REQ_CANCEL\n");
3951#endif
3952 break;
3953 case DI_REQ_CANCEL|DI_REQ_PROCESS:
3954 /* ÄÌÍÑ°õºşÍ×µá¡Ü¥¸¥ç¥Ö¥­¥ã¥ó¥»¥ëÍ×µá */
3955 aspara.jobreset = prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = TRUE;
3956#ifdef DEBUG_JOBREST
3957 PRINTF("prcall_continue DI_REQ_CANCEL|DI_REQ_PROCESS\n");
3958#endif
3959 break ;
3960
3961 /* ¥×¥í¥°¥é¥àÅĞÏ¿Í×µá */
3962 case DI_REQ_PROGENTRY :
3963 aspara.jobreset = prcall_ext_info.forced_job_reset = FALSE;

4581void *prcall_realloc(void *data_ptr, size_t size)
4582{
4583 unsigned char * data;
4584 if( size == 0 ) {
4585 prcall_free(data_ptr);
4586 return NULL;
4587 }
4588
4589 if( !data_ptr ) {
4590 return prcall_malloc(size);
4591 }
4592
4593 data = pr_memory_realloc(
4594 ((prif_dest_ptr)(prcall_ext_info_ptr->dest))->prh,
4595 (unsigned char*)data_ptr,
4596 size);
4597#ifdef DEBUG_MEMORY
4598 BGMSG(("prcall_realloc %d 0x%08x=>0x%08x\n", size, data_ptr, data));
4599#endif /* DEBUG_MEMORY */
4600 return (void *)data;
4601}

4957 /*

4960 * GPS¤Ç¤ÏÌµ¤¯¤Æ¤â¥¨¥é¡¼ÍúÎò¤¬¹Ô¤ï¤ì¤ë¤¬¡¢nGPS¤Ç¤Ï»ÅÍÍ¤¬ÊÑ¹¹¤µ¤ì¤¿¡£

4964 */
4965 if (status != PRCALL_STATUS_JOBRESET) {

4967 }
4968 }

4971 * ´û¤Ë¥¨¥é¡¼¤¬È¯À¸¤·¤Æ¤¤¤ë¾ì¹ç¤Ë¤Ï¡¢¥Ç¡¼¥¿¤ÏÆÉ¤ß¼Î¤Æ¤ëÉ¬Í×¤¬Ìµ¤¤
4972 */
4973 data_reset = 0;
4974 }
4975 if (prcall_ext_info_ptr->status & PRCALL_STATUS_JOBSTART) {

4977 prcall_ext_info.job_reseted = TRUE;
4978 }
4979 }
4980 /*
4981 * Àè¤Ë¥¨¥é¡¼¥¹¥Æ¡¼¥¿¥¹¤òÀßÄê¤·¤Æ¤ª¤¯

4986 * EOF¤Ş¤¿¤Ï¥¿¥¤¥à¥¢¥¦¥È¤Ş¤ÇÆÉ¤ß¼Î¤Æ¤ë
4987 */
4988 DBG_MSG_JOBRESET("data discard start");
4989 reset_job();
4990 DBG_MSG_JOBRESET("data discard end\n");
4991 }
4992 }
4993 else {
4994 /*
4995 * Àµ¾ï°õºş»ş¤Î¥¹¥Æ¡¼¥¿¥¹¤òÈ¿±Ç¤¹¤ë
4996 */
4997
4998 /* ¥ï¡¼¥Ë¥ó¥°¤ÎÂĞ±ş 2006/07/05 h.funaki */
4999 if ( status == PRCALL_STATUS_WARNING ) {
5000#ifdef USE_MP_TIFF
5001 if (notify_warning_message) {
5002 di_notify_msg(DI_NOTIFYMSG_ERRFORCE, DI_ST_99_WARNING);
5003 }
5004#else
5005 di_notify_msg(DI_NOTIFYMSG_ERRFORCE, DI_ST_99_WARNING);
5006#endif
5007 }
5008 else {
5009 if (status == PRCALL_STATUS_DATA_WAIT) {
5010 prcall_ext_info.job_reseted = FALSE;
5011 }
5012 prcall_ext_info_ptr->status = status;
5013 if (status == PRCALL_STATUS_SEARCH_PJL) {
5014 reset_job();
5015 }
5016 }

5019}

5038int prcall_check_paper_direction(imagedraw_paper_info_t *paper_request, int mode)
5039{

5041 unsigned char paper_id;
5042 unsigned char kind;
5043 environment_page_t penv_page;
5044 int stat; /* Éüµ¢¾ğÊó */
5045 int result;
5046
5047 DBG_MSG_PRCALL("prcall_check_paper_direction ");
5048
5049#ifdef GPS
5050 get_pageinfo(&penv_page, 0, 0); /* ¥Ú¡¼¥¸ÍÑ´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤Î¼èÆÀ */
5051

5056 */

5064 }

5066 penv_page.paper_type = paper_request->kind;
5067 kind = paper_request->kind;
5068 }
5069 else {
5070 penv_page.paper_type = DI_PAPER_AUTO;
5071 kind = PRCALL_PAPER_TYPE_ALLRANGE_SELECT; /* »æ¼ï¤Ë¤è¤é¤º¸¡º÷¤¹¤ë */
5072 }
5073 if (flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_SIZE) {
5074 /*
5075 * »æ¥µ¥¤¥º»ØÄê¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
5076 * ´Ä¶­ÊÑ¿ô¤Ï¾å½ñ¤­¤µ¤ì¤ë¡£
5077 */

5079 penv_page.paper_length = paper_request->length;

5096
5097 if ((flag & IMAGEDRAW_PAPER_REQUEST_PAPER_ID) == 0) {

5099 /*
5100 *

5102 paper_request->tray_id = penv_page.input_tray;
5103 }
5104 }
5105 }
5106#else
5107 /*
5108 * ¼Âµ¡°Ê³°¤Ç¤Ï¡¢¾ï¤Ë»ØÄêÊı¸ş¤ÎÍÑ»æ¤¬¤¢¤ë¤³¤È¤òÄÌÃÎ¤¹¤ë¡£
5109 */
5110 stat = PRCALL_PAPER_DIRECTION_EXACT;
5111#endif
5112 return stat;
5113}
5114/*
5115 * ÂçÊ¸»ú->¾®Ê¸»úÊÑ´¹
5116 *} Éüµ¢¾ğÊó¡¡:'\0'¤ò´Ş¤àÊ¸»úÎó¤ÎÄ¹¤µ
5117 */
5118int prsub_convert_strings(unsigned char *dest, const unsigned char *src)
5119{
5120 int i;
5121 for (i = 0; i < 512; i++) {
5122 if ('A' <= *src && *src <= 'Z')
5123 *dest = *src + 'a' - 'A';
5124 else {
5125 *dest = *src;
5126 }
5127 if (*src == '\0')
5128 break;
5129 dest++;
5130 src++;
5131 }
5132
5133 return i;
5134
5135}
5136
5137char * prsub_strstr (const char * str1, const char * str2)
5138{
5139 char *cp = (char *) str1;
5140 char *s1, *s2;
5141
5142 if ( !*str2 )
5143 return((char *)str1);
5144
5145 while (*cp)
5146 {
5147 s1 = cp;
5148 s2 = (char *) str2;
5149
5150 while ( *s1 && *s2 && !(*s1-*s2) )
5151 s1++, s2++;
5152
5153 if (!*s2)
5154 return(cp);
5155
5156 cp++;
5157 }
5158
5159 return(NULL);
5160
5161}

5276int prcall_set_extend_data(unsigned short type, void *data)
5277{
5278 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
5279 int i;
5280 unsigned long mask;
5281 unsigned long flag;
5282 int result;
5283 /*
5284 * ¥«¥á¥é¥á¥â¤ÎÆâÍÆ¤Ï¡¢pDest¤Î³ÈÄ¥¾ğÊóÎÎ°è¤Ë³ÊÇ¼¤¹¤ë¡£
5285 */
5286#ifdef USE_USERFORM
5287 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_CURRENT); /* ¸½ºß¥«¥ì¥ó¥È¤ÎpDest¤ò¼èÆÀ¤¹¤ë¡£ */
5288#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
5289 pDest = prcall_get_dest();
5290#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
5291 mask = 0x00000ff;
5292 flag = pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_flag;
5293 result = -1;
5294 for (i = 0; i < EXTEND_DATA_SET_Area_MAX; i++) {
5295 if ((flag & mask) == 0) {
5296 pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_data [i] = (unsigned char *)data;
5297 pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_flag |= EXTEND_DATA_SET_Area(type, i);
5298 result = 0;
5299 break;
5300 }
5301 mask <<= 8;
5302 }
5303 return result;
5304}
5305void *prcall_get_extend_data(unsigned short type)
5306{
5307 prif_dest_ptr pDest;
5308 int i;
5309 unsigned long mask;
5310 unsigned char *data;
5311 unsigned short data_type;
5312 unsigned long flag;
5313
5314#ifdef USE_USERFORM
5315 pDest = prcall_get_dest(PRCALL_DESTNATION_INFO_CURRENT); /* ¸½ºß¥«¥ì¥ó¥È¤ÎpDest¤ò¼èÆÀ¤¹¤ë¡£ */
5316#else /* !USE_USERFORM */
5317 pDest = prcall_get_dest();
5318#endif /* USE_USERFORM */
5319 mask = 0x00000ff;
5320 data = NULL;
5321 flag = pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_flag;
5322 for (i = 0; i < EXTEND_DATA_SET_Area_MAX; i++) {
5323 if ((flag & mask) != 0) {
5324 data_type = EXTEND_DATA_GET_Area(flag, i);
5325 if (data_type == type) {
5326 /*
5327 * ¸½¾õIDP¤Ç¤Ï¥Ç¡¼¥¿¼ïÊÌ1¤ò¥«¥á¥é¥á¥â¾ğÊó¤È¤·¤Æ»ÈÍÑ¤¹¤ë¡£
5328 * ¥«¥á¥é¥á¥â¤Ï»ÈÍÑ¤·¤¿¤é²òÊü¤¹¤ëÉ¬Í×¤¬¤¢¤ë¡£
5329 */
5330 data = pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_data [i];
5331 pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_data [i] = NULL;
5332 EXTEND_DATA_CLEAR_Area(flag, i);
5333 break;
5334 }
5335 }
5336 mask <<= 8;
5337 }
5338 if (data != NULL) {
5339 pDest->page_info.source_info.extend_flag = flag;
5340 }
5341 return data;
5342}

5403/*****************************************************************************
5404* Name : CheckPrintMode()
5405* Function : °õºş¥â¡¼¥É¤Î¥Á¥§¥Ã¥¯

5409* Output : none
5410* Return : ¡á1¡§OK
5411* : ¡á0¡§NG
5412* Note : »ØÄê¤µ¤ì¤¿¥Ñ¥ì¥á¡¼¥¿¤Ç°õºş¥â¡¼¥É¤ÎÀßÄê¤¬²ÄÇ½¤«¥Á¥§¥Ã¥¯¤¹¤ë¡£

5414LONG CheckPrintMode( LONG dpi, LONG p_kind, LONG Quality )
5415{

5418 resolution_info_t *reso_ptr;
5419
5420 reso_ptr = devinfo.reso_set;
5421 /* ²òÁüÅÙ¥Æ¡¼¥Ö¥ë¤Ë»ØÄê¤µ¤ì¤¿¥Ñ¥é¥á¡¼¥¿¤ÎÁÈ¤ß¹ç¤ï¤»¤¢¤ë¤«¥Á¥§¥Ã¥¯¤¹¤ë¡£ */
5422 for (i = 0 ; i < devinfo.resonum; i++, reso_ptr++) {
5423 if (( reso_ptr->x == dpi ) && ( reso_ptr->y == dpi ) && /* ²òÁüÅÙ */
5424 ( reso_ptr->paper == p_kind ) && /* »æ¼ï¥°¥ë¡¼¥× */
5425 ( reso_ptr->prt_mode == Quality ) ) { /* °õºşÉÊ¼Á*/
5426 break ;
5427 }
5428 }
5429
5430 /* ÁÈ¹ç¤»¥Á¥§¥Ã¥¯ */
5431 if ( i < devinfo.resonum ) {
5432 return( 1 ) ;
5433 }
5434 else {
5435 return( 0 ) ;
5436 }
5437
5438}

5541static int _URF2PR(urf_pr table[], unsigned char urf_val, int *pr_val)
5542{
5543 int i;
5544 for(i = 0; table[i].urf != -1; i++){
5545 if(table[i].urf == urf_val){
5546 *pr_val = table[i].pr;
5547 break;
5548 }
5549 }
5550 if (table[i].urf == -1) {
5551 return 0;
5552 }
5553 else {
5554 return 1;
5555 }
5556}
5557
5558int getUrfPHead_PrVal(int urf_phead_id, int *pr_val)
5559{
5560 urfPageHead *urfPHead;
5561 extern urfPageHead *getUrfPageHeader(void);
5562 int def_flag = 0;
5563 int result;
5564 int i;
5565
5566 urfPHead = getUrfPageHeader();
5567 if ((urfPHead == NULL) || (pr_val == NULL)) {
5568 return 0;
5569 }
5570
5571 switch (urf_phead_id) {
5572 case URF_PAGEHEAD_DUPLEX:
5573 if (urfPHead->duplex == 0) {
5574 def_flag = 1;
5575 }
5576 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_duplex, urfPHead->duplex, pr_val);
5577 break;
5578 case URF_PAGEHEAD_MEDIA:
5579 if (urfPHead->media == 0) {
5580 def_flag = 1;
5581 }
5582 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_paper_type, urfPHead->media, pr_val);
5583 break;
5584 case URF_PAGEHEAD_INTRAY:
5585 if (urfPHead->intray == 0) {
5586 def_flag = 1;
5587 }
5588 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_input_tray, urfPHead->intray, pr_val);
5589 break;
5590 case URF_PAGEHEAD_OUTBIN:
5591 if (urfPHead->outbin == 0) {
5592 def_flag = 1;
5593 }
5594 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_output_tray, urfPHead->outbin, pr_val);
5595 break;
5596 case URF_PAGEHEAD_COPIES:
5597 if (urfPHead->copies == 0) {
5598 def_flag = 1;
5599 }
5600 *pr_val = urfPHead->copies;
5601 break;
5602 case URF_PAGEHEAD_STAPLE:
5603 for (i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
5604 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_staple, urfPHead->finishngs[i], pr_val);
5605 if (result) {
5606 break;
5607 }
5608 }
5609 break;
5610 case URF_PAGEHEAD_PUNCH:
5611 for (i = 0; i < 4; i++) {
5612 result = _URF2PR(urf_pr_punch, urfPHead->finishngs[i], pr_val);
5613 if (result) {
5614 break;
5615 }
5616 }
5617 break;
5618 default:
5619 result = 0;
5620 break;
5621 }
5622
5623 return (result && !def_flag);
5624}
5625#endif /* USE_MP_TIFF */
